beginSubroutine: s32'cosShotCheck'
  ifPlayerCharacter: s16'cos'
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(0)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
          runOnObject: (PLAYER)
            storeValue: Mem(CPUVal7), Val(1)
          endRunOnObject: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        runOnObject: (PLAYER)
          storeValue: Mem(CPUVal7), Val(1)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        storeValue: Mem(CPUVal7), Val(0)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmn_TrialTokeiMain'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    linkObjPosition: 3
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Mem(SentToObject0)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(SentToObject1)
    ifPlayerCharacter: s16'cos'
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        storeValue: Mem(CPUVal7), Val(0)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
    upon: (SIGNAL0)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(1)
      if: Mem(ActReg0)
        callPrivateFunction: s32'TrialReadyGo', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0
      endIf: 
      else: 
        if: Mem(ActReg1)
        endIf: 
        callPrivateFunction: s32'TrialReadyGo', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0
        deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_TrialTokeiMain'
      endElse: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (IDLING)
      callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cosShotCheck', Val(1), Val(1), Val(0), Val(0)
      if: Mem(ActReg2)
        if: Mem(ActReg0)
          if: Mem(TrialReadyGo)
            if: Mem(ActReg1)
            endIf: 
            deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_TrialTokeiMain'
            callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cosShotCheck', Val(0), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_MissionCtrl'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    sendValuesToObject: 2, 115, 0, 1
    createObjectWithArg: s32'cmn_TrialTokeiMain', (PLAYER)
    stackObject: (STACK0), (PREVIOUS)
    missionSealAll: 1
    missionSealAttack: 1
    missionEnemyCpuStop: 1
    if: Mem(SentToObject1)
      missionSealFDash: 0
    endIf: 
    upon: (IDLING)
      isObjectActive: (STACK0)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        if: Mem(TrialTumbleNum)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
          ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(180)
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (MISSION_FAIL)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(TrialTumbleNum), Val(1)
        sendSignalToAction: s32'cmn_TrialTokeiMain', (SIGNAL0)
        missionKeyStart: -1
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
      missionMiss: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_MissionCMN_000'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    sendValuesToObject: 2, 115, 0, 1
    createObjectWithArg: s32'cmn_TrialTokeiMain', (PLAYER)
    stackObject: (STACK0), (PREVIOUS)
    missionSealAll: 1
    missionSealAttack: 1
    storeValue: Mem(TrialExVal0), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(TrialExVal1), Val(0)
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      storeValue: Mem(BurstVal), Val(0)
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (ENEMY)
      storeValue: Mem(BurstVal), Val(0)
    endRunOnObject: 
    upon: (IDLING)
      isObjectActive: (STACK0)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        if: Mem(TrialExVal1)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(TrialExVal0), Val(1)
          debugLogForScript: s32'time', 2, 222
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        if: Mem(TrialTumbleNum)
          missionSealAll: 0
          missionSealJump: 1
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
          ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(150)
            missionMiss: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(TrialTumbleNum), Val(2)
            runOnObject: (PLAYER)
              storeValue: Mem(TrialExVal0), Mem(EnemyDistanceX)
            endRunOnObject: 
            ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(TrialExVal0), Val(130000)
              missionFail: s32'Tikaduke'
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (MISSION_FAIL)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(TrialTumbleNum), Val(1)
        sendSignalToAction: s32'cmn_TrialTokeiMain', (SIGNAL0)
        missionKeyStart: -1
        storeValue: Mem(TrialExVal1), Val(1)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
endState:

        endIf:

        missionKeyStart: -1

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnPositiveBonusStart'
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg6), Val(1)
  storeValue: Mem(PlayerAttackRate), Val(110)
  storeValue: Mem(PlayerDefenceRate), Val(110)
  setStatusIcon: 1, 1
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnPositiveBonusEnd'
  if: Mem(CmnCharaReg6)
    addTensionBalance: 0, -12500
  endIf: 
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg6), Val(0)
  storeValue: Mem(PlayerAttackRate), Val(100)
  storeValue: Mem(PlayerDefenceRate), Val(100)
  setStatusIcon: 1, 0
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnGuardInit'
  guardTension: 20, 40, 60, 80, 100
  instantBlockTension: 100
  faultlessDefenseGuardStop: 0, 0
  faultlessDefenseGuardTension: 250, 300, 350, 400, 450, 25
  setFDConstantMeterDrain: 25, 50
  faultlessDefensePushback: 120, 80, 120
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnRoundInit'
  health: 420
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    health: 10000
  endIf: 
  initJumpMotionFrame: 9, 9, 9, 9, 9, 9
  initHomingJumpMaxYSpeed: 1750
  initHomingJumpMaxXSpeed: 5250
  initHomingJumpXReduce: 16
  initHomingJumpYOffset: 52500
  homingJumpYOffsetRED: 0
  stunResistance: 60
  critical: 0
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnTensionBalanceInit'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnGuardInit'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnAfroInit'
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    materialValResetOnActionChange: 31, 0
    if: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
      storeValue: Mem(To3IsSkillCursorStop), Val(2)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmn_JustGuardobj_hontai'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_JustGuardobj_hontai'
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_JustGuardobj_shot'
    upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK)
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endUpon: 
    upon: (PLAYER_GUARD)
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endUpon: 
    upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        pushboxFix: 0
      endRunOnObject: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Guard_Chokuzen'
  createParticle: s32'cmn_guard_just', (PLAYER)
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  upon: (PRE_DRAW)
    ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(PlayerDamage)
      ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(PlayerDamageOrGuard)
        runOnObject: (PLAYER)
          pushboxFix: 1
          ignorePushback: 1
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_JustGuardobj_shot'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_JustGuardobj_hontai'
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_JustGuardobj_shot'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 10
  cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Guard_Chokuzen'
  createParticle: s32'cmn_guard_just', (PLAYER)
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FPGuardobj_hontai'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_FPGuardobj_hontai'
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_FPGuardobj_shot'
    upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK)
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endUpon: 
    upon: (PLAYER_GUARD)
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endUpon: 
    upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        pushboxFix: 0
      endRunOnObject: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  upon: (PRE_DRAW)
    ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(PlayerDamage)
      ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(PlayerDamageOrGuard)
        runOnObject: (PLAYER)
          pushboxFix: 1
          ignorePushback: 1
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FPGuardobj_shot'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_FPGuardobj_hontai'
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_FPGuardobj_shot'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 10
endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_3on3_SkillCondition'
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
      addMoveFlag: (IS_MAIN_PLAYER)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)
      addMoveFlag: 120
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(4)
      addMoveFlag: 120
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(5)
      addMoveFlag: (IS_MAIN_PLAYER)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(6)
      addMoveFlag: 120
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnEntryToStand1P'
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Mem(FuncArg0)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(FuncArg1)
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    zLine: 5, 5
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      zLine: 4, 5
    endRunOnObject: 
    setEventTrigger: (TIMER), 85
    upon: (TIMER)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (TIMER)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_EXIT)
      runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
        zLine: 2, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
        zLine: 6, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
        zLine: 5, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        zLine: 0, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
        zLine: 6, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
        zLine: 5, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (AFTER_EXIT)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_EXIT)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (TIMER)
      runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
        zLine: 2, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
        zLine: 6, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
        zLine: 5, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        zLine: 0, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
        zLine: 6, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
        zLine: 5, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnEntryToStand2P'
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Mem(FuncArg0)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(FuncArg1)
  upon: (IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(0)
      displayModel: 0
      lockScreenPosition: 1
      checkScreenCollision: 0
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(1)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnEntryToStandEx'
      setPositionXInBattle: -402000
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-252000), Val(0), Mem(ActReg1)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Val(-2500), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(PosZ)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 2500
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Mem(ActReg0)
      displayModel: 1
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Mem(ActReg1)
      lockScreenPosition: 0
      checkScreenCollision: 1
      physicsXImpulse: 0, 0
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setPositionXInBattle: -252000
      setDepth: 0
      haltMomentum: 1
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    zLine: 4, 5
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnEntryToStandEx'
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg2), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(ActReg0)
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg3), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(ActReg1)
  ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg3), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnactroundwin'
  setEventTrigger: (TIMER), 1
  upon: (TIMER)
    if: Mem(IsTo3)
      if: Mem(IsSubMember1Self)
        zLine: 6, 5
        checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2), s32'CmnActRoundWin'
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2), Mem(PosZ)
          ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Mem(Tmp)
            zLine: 6, 5
            runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
              zLine: 5, 5
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2), Mem(PosZ)
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(PosZ), Mem(Tmp)
            zLine: 5, 5
            runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
              zLine: 6, 5
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      if: Mem(IsSubMember2Self)
        zLine: 5, 5
        checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1), s32'CmnActRoundWin'
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1), Mem(PosZ)
          ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Mem(Tmp)
            zLine: 6, 5
            runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
              zLine: 5, 5
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1), Mem(PosZ)
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(PosZ), Mem(Tmp)
            zLine: 5, 5
            runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
              zLine: 6, 5
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    setEventTrigger: (TIMER), 2
    upon: (TIMER)
      setNoCollision: 1
      pushboxCollisionSameSide: 1
      ifNot: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
        pushCollisionOnPlayersOnly: 0
        checkCurrentStateName: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), s32'CmnActMatchWin'
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          jumpToState: s32'AssistResult'
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        if: Mem(IsTo3)
          ifNot: Mem(Timeup)
            runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
              setNoCollision: 0
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
      upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
        if: Mem(IsTo3)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(2)
            setPushboxWidth: 165000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(3)
            setPushboxWidth: 180000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(4)
            setPushboxWidth: 195000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(5)
            setPushboxWidth: 210000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(6)
            setPushboxWidth: 225000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(7)
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        else: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(2)
            setPushboxWidth: 150000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(3)
            setPushboxWidth: 160000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(4)
            setPushboxWidth: 170000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(5)
            setPushboxWidth: 180000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(6)
            setPushboxWidth: 190000
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(7)
            setPushboxWidth: 200000
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
          endIf: 
        endElse: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnactlose'
  setEventTrigger: (TIMER), 2
  upon: (TIMER)
    setNoCollision: 1
    pushboxCollisionSameSide: 1
    ifNot: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
      checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), s32'CmnActMatchWin'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        jumpToState: s32'AssistResult'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), s32'CmnActMatchWin'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'matchlose'
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
    upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(2)
        setPushboxWidth: 150000
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(3)
        setPushboxWidth: 160000
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(4)
        setPushboxWidth: 170000
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(5)
        setPushboxWidth: 180000
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(6)
        setPushboxWidth: 190000
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(7)
        setPushboxWidth: 200000
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnOnActionBeginPre'
  if: Mem(BattleDoing)
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_changecheck', Val(0), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  endIf: 
  else: 
    if: Mem(IsTo3)
      ifNot: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
        checkScreenCollision: 0
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endElse: 
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    ifNot: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(PosZ), Val(0)
        zLine: 1, 5
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnOnActionBegin'
  if: Mem(BattleDoing)
    if: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
      pushCollisionOnPlayersOnly: 0
      if: Mem(PlayerDamage)
        ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg29), Val(2)
          pushCollisionOnPlayersOnly: 1
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      if: Mem(IsTo3)
        suikomare: 0
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    if: Mem(IsTo3)
      if: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
        ifNot: Mem(HitPoint)
          ifNot: Mem(MatchEnd)
            setNoCollision: 0
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endElse: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnOnFrameStep'
  checkCurrentStateName: (PLAYER), s32'CmnActRomanCancel'
  ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
    checkInput: (INPUT_66_QUICK)
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      checkInput: (INPUT_6_ELM_TRG)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(6)
        ifNot: Mem(CtrlDir)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(1)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(2)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    checkInput: (INPUT_44_QUICK)
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      checkInput: (INPUT_4_ELM_TRG)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(4)
        ifNot: Mem(CtrlDir)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(1)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(2)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    checkInput: (INPUT_22)
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      checkInput: (INPUT_2_ELM_TRG)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    checkInput: (INPUT_88)
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      checkInput: (INPUT_8_ELM_TRG)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(8)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    checkInput: (INPUT_DASH_STRICT)
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(6)
      checkInput: (INPUT_6)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(6)
        ifNot: Mem(CtrlDir)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(1)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(2)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
      checkInput: (INPUT_4)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(4)
        ifNot: Mem(CtrlDir)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(1)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(2)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
      checkInput: (INPUT_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(2)
      endIf: 
      checkInput: (INPUT_8)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(8)
      endIf: 
      checkInput: (INPUT_1)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(0)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(0)
      endIf: 
      checkInput: (INPUT_3)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(0)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(0)
      endIf: 
      checkInput: (INPUT_7)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(0)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(0)
      endIf: 
      checkInput: (INPUT_9)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(0)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(0)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    if: Mem(CmnCharaReg8)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(100)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(100)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(10)
      endIf: 
      ifNot: Mem(CheckStop)
        ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg31)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(-1)
          ifOperation: (MOD_EQUALS_0), Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(200)
            storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg8), Val(0)
            storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg10), Val(0)
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(IsRoundTimerStop)
    if: Mem(CmnCharaReg6)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(Tension), Val(10000)
        addTension: 2
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(TensionBalance), Val(25000)
        addTensionBalance: 0, 50
      endIf: 
      modifyBurstGauge: 12
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  if: Mem(CmnCharaReg9)
    if: Mem(IsLand)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg9), Val(0)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    if: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
      isObjectActive: (STACK_CMN_ACT)
      ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
        createObject: s32'cmnWSBDummy', (PLAYER)
        stackObject: (STACK_CMN_ACT), (PREVIOUS)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    isObjectActive: (STACK_CMN_ACT)
    ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
      createObject: s32'cmnWSBDummy', (PLAYER)
      stackObject: (STACK_CMN_ACT), (PREVIOUS)
    endIf: 
  endElse: 
  ifNot: Mem(PlayerDamage)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg30), Val(0)
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    deactivateObjectByNameExceptSelf: s32'cmnWSBDummy'
    upon: (PRE_DRAW)
      ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(15)
        storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Dir), (PLAYER), Mem(Dir)
        storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(PosXRaw), (PLAYER), Mem(PosXRaw)
        storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(PosY), (PLAYER), Mem(PosY)
        storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(PosZ), (PLAYER), Mem(PosZ)
      endIf: 
      if: Mem(IsTo3)
        ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
          deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_wall_dir'
  if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
    upon: (WALL)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (WALL)
      fadeOutStart: 1000, 0
      pushboxFix: 1
      if: Mem(IsTo3)
        checkScreenCollision: 0
      endIf: 
      checkMoveFlag: (CLOSE_TO_LEFT_CORNER)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        faceRight: 
      endIf: 
      checkMoveFlag: (CLOSE_TO_RIGHT_CORNER)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        faceLeft: 
      endIf: 
      screenAdditionalWidth: -10000
      addPositionX: 0, -10000
      checkLastAttackHitStateName: 3, s32'ABA_SP1_Land_exe'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        addPositionX: 0, -50000
      endIf: 
      checkLastAttackHitStateName: 3, s32'ABA_SP1_Land_Moroha_exe'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        addPositionX: 0, -50000
      endIf: 
      checkLastAttackHitStateName: 3, s32'ABA_SP1_Air_exe'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        addPositionX: 0, -50000
      endIf: 
      checkLastAttackHitStateName: 3, s32'ABA_SP1_Air_Moroha_exe'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        addPositionX: 0, -50000
      endIf: 
      addPositionY: 0, 1
      hitBeckReturnIgnoreAll: 1
      wallTouchTime: 
      invulnForce: 1
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        invulnForce: 1
      endRunOnObject: 
      upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
          ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(CheckStop), Val(3)
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
            invulnForce: 0
            runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
              invulnForce: 0
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(2)
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
            invulnForce: 0
            runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
              invulnForce: 0
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
  upon: (AFTER_RECEIVE_HIT)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_RECEIVE_HIT)
    ifNotInObject: (ATTACKER), Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
      storeValue: Mem(ForceWSBFlag), Val(1)
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

    isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)

      runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
        resetMotionBlurAmount: 
        deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
    isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)

      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
        resetMotionBlurAmount: 
        deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
      endRunOnObject:

    if: Mem(Tmp)

endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkLv0'
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    initializeAttackCategoryByCurrent: 
  endIf: 
  attackLevel: 0
  hitstunAmount: 12
  blockstunAmount: 9
  riscGain: 5
  ifNot: Mem(IsPlayer)
    riscGain: 5
    attackReflect: 1
    attackFrontDirection: 0
    attackIgnoreCaution: 1
  endIf: 
  riscConsume: 10
  prorationTandan: 0
  hitStop: 11
  ifNot: Mem(FuncArg3)
    tensionGainOnConnect: 30
  endIf: 
  else: 
    tensionGainOnConnect: 15
  endIf: 
  preGuardRange: 0, 190
  preGuardRangeY: 0, 250
  rollCount: 1
  if: Mem(IsLand)
    hitAirPushbackX: 0, 21500
    hitAirPushbackY: 0, 30000
    hitGravity: Val(3000)
  endIf: 
  else: 
    hitAirPushbackX: 0, 21500
    hitAirPushbackY: 0, 10000
    hitGravity: Val(3500)
  endElse: 
  forcedComboScaleCount: 5
  considerHitAirPushbackX: 15
  considerHitAirPushbackY: 15
  airGuardPushbackX: 0
  faultlessDefenseMinimumPushback: 75
  guardCrushPushback: 50
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    wallPushback: 250
  endIf: 
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    guardLandingAction: 1
    airBlockstunAddition: 15
  endIf: 
  attackPositiveBonus: 1
  upon: (COUNTER_HIT)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (COUNTER_HIT)
    if: Mem(IsPlayer)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmn_RISCounter'
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnAtk_GB_TGG', Mem(FuncArg0), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(1), Mem(FuncArg3)
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_SameAttack', Val(2), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  endIf: 
  else: 
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_SameAttack', Val(1), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  endElse: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkLv1'
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    initializeAttackCategoryByCurrent: 
  endIf: 
  attackLevel: 1
  hitstunAmount: 14
  blockstunAmount: 11
  riscGain: 10
  ifNot: Mem(IsPlayer)
    riscGain: 5
    attackReflect: 1
    attackFrontDirection: 0
    attackIgnoreCaution: 1
  endIf: 
  riscConsume: 10
  prorationTandan: 0
  hitStop: 12
  ifNot: Mem(FuncArg3)
    tensionGainOnConnect: 40
  endIf: 
  else: 
    tensionGainOnConnect: 20
  endIf: 
  preGuardRange: 0, 195
  preGuardRangeY: 0, 250
  rollCount: 1
  if: Mem(IsLand)
    hitAirPushbackX: 0, 21500
    hitAirPushbackY: 0, 30000
    hitGravity: Val(3000)
  endIf: 
  else: 
    hitAirPushbackX: 0, 21500
    hitAirPushbackY: 0, 10000
    hitGravity: Val(3500)
  endElse: 
  forcedComboScaleCount: 5
  considerHitAirPushbackX: 15
  considerHitAirPushbackY: 15
  airGuardPushbackX: 0
  faultlessDefenseMinimumPushback: 75
  guardCrushPushback: 50
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    wallPushback: 250
  endIf: 
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    guardLandingAction: 1
    airBlockstunAddition: 15
  endIf: 
  attackPositiveBonus: 1
  upon: (COUNTER_HIT)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (COUNTER_HIT)
    if: Mem(IsPlayer)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmn_RISCounter'
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnAtk_GB_TGG', Mem(FuncArg0), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(2), Mem(FuncArg3)
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_SameAttack', Val(2), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  endIf: 
  else: 
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_SameAttack', Val(1), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)

endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv0'
  wallDamage: 0
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg13)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg13), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Val(0), Mem(CmnCharaReg13), Mem(CmnCharaActReg6)
  attackExHitParam: Mem(CmnCharaActReg6), 0, 10000, 1, (ENEMY), Mem(WSBPoint)
  ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), (ENEMY), Mem(PosXRaw), Val(750000)
    ifOperationInObject: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), (ENEMY), Mem(PosXRaw), Val(-750000)
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), (ENEMY), Mem(WSBPoint), Val(1750)
        attackExHitParam: Mem(CmnCharaActReg6), 0, 1500, 1, (ENEMY), Mem(WSBPoint)
        disableWallBreak: 1
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  if: Mem(AdjustmentForScript0)
    debugLogForScript: s32'WSB_Add_Lv0', 0, 0
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_hosei'
  if: Mem(AdjustmentForScript0)
    debugLogForScript: s32'-------------------------------', 0, 0
    debugLogForScript: s32'cmn_hosei', 0, 0
    debugLogForScript: s32'VAR_CmnCharaReg12', 2, 339
    debugLogForScript: s32'VAR_CmnCharaReg13', 2, 340
  endIf: 
  modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000000)
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000000)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD_EQUALS_0), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(100000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(10000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(100000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(10000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(1)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv3'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(100), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv5'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(10), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv5'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv5'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000000)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD_EQUALS_0), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv0'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(100000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(1)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv1'
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(10000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
      ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv3'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    if: Mem(AdjustmentForScript0)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
        ifOperation: (MOD_EQUALS_0), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
          debugLogForScript: s32'airattack', 0, 0
        endIf: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(100000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
        ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
          debugLogForScript: s32'p', 0, 0
        endIf: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(10000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
        ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
          debugLogForScript: s32'k_gedan', 0, 0
        endIf: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
        ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
          debugLogForScript: s32'chudan', 0, 0
        endIf: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(100000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
        ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
          debugLogForScript: s32'gedan_or_taikuu', 0, 0
        endIf: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(10000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
        ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
          debugLogForScript: s32'shot', 0, 0
        endIf: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
        ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
          debugLogForScript: s32'muteki', 0, 0
        endIf: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(100), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)
        ifOperation: (MOD), Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(2)
          debugLogForScript: s32'land', 0, 0
        endIf: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(10), Mem(CmnCharaReg12)

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_AttackEnd'
  attackEndDelay: 
  checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'NmlAtk5CFar'
  ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
    checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'NmlAtk2C'
    ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
      checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'NmlAtkAir5C'
      ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
        checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'NmlAtk5D'
        ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
          checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'NmlAtk2D'
          ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
            checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'NmlAtk6D'
            ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
              checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'NmlAtkAir5D'
              ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
                enableGatlings: 0
                enableWhiffCancel: 0
                whiffCancelNext: 0
              endIf: 
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_RISCounter'

    damageEffect: 4, s32'cmn_counterhit_large'
    doubleSlashEffectBugFix: 1
    battleStats: s32'CounterHitRisc_Atk', 0, 1
    runOnObject: (DEFENDER)
      battleStats: s32'CounterHitRisc_Dmg', 0, 1
    endRunOnObject: 
    counterHitProcess: (RISC)
    sendValuesToObject: 0, 1, 0, 0
    createObjectWithArg: s32'cmnHiCounterCamera', (PLAYER)
    uiMessage: 43
    narratorVoiceLine: s32'Btl_Counter'
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

      ifNotInObject: (DEFENDER), Mem(IsRISCCounterHit)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (COUNTER_HIT)
        slowHitstop: 1, 1

        damageEffect: 4, s32'cmn_counterhit_middle'
        battleStats: s32'CounterHitM_Atk', 0, 1
        runOnObject: (DEFENDER)
          battleStats: s32'CounterHitM_Dmg', 0, 1
        endRunOnObject: 
        counterHitProcess: (MEDIUM)
        createObject: s32'cmnCounterCamera', (PLAYER)
        narratorVoiceLine: s32'Btl_Counter'
        cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
        callSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterSlowSettings'
      endIf: 
      callSubroutine: s32'cmn_RISCounter'
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginState: s32'cmnCounterCamera'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    upon: (PRE_DRAW)
      modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg7), Val(1)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg7), Val(2)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PRE_DRAW)
        storeValue: Mem(ObjReg1), Val(1)
        ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(PlayerDamage)
          storeValue: Mem(ObjReg1), Val(0)
        endIf: 
        ifNotInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(HitPoint)
          storeValue: Mem(ObjReg1), Val(0)
        endIf: 
        if: Mem(IsWorldStopperOther)
          storeValue: Mem(ObjReg1), Val(0)
        endIf: 
        if: Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
          storeValue: Mem(ObjReg1), Val(0)
        endIf: 
        if: Mem(ObjReg1)
          storeValue: Mem(ObjReg1), Val(0)
          if: Mem(IsEnemySlow)
            runOnObject: (PLAYER)
              addSlowdown: 10
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          ifNot: Mem(SentToObject0)
            runOnObject: (PLAYER)
              superFreeze: 9, 119, 20, 20
              addSlowdown: 25
              fadeOutStart: 1000, 0
              whiffCancelOptionBufferTime: s32'RomanCancelAttack', 18
              ignoreSuperFreeze: 0
              ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 0
              ignoreSpeedTime: 1
              hitStopTime: 
            endRunOnObject: 
            runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
              ignoreSuperFreeze: 0
              ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 0
              ignoreSpeedTime: 1
              hitStopTime: 
            endRunOnObject: 
            ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 1
            ignoreSlowdown: 1
            particleSlowdown: 30, 100
            setMotionBlurAmount: 300
            cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_SlowHitstop1'
            upon: (PRE_DRAW)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
              ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CheckStop), Val(2)
                storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
              endIf: 
              if: Mem(ActReg1)
                clearRegisteredUponCode: (PRE_DRAW)
                runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
                  hitStopTime: 
                endRunOnObject: 
              endIf: 
              modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg2), Val(1)
              ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(3)
                clearRegisteredUponCode: (PRE_DRAW)
              endIf: 
              callSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterSlowSettings'
            endUpon: 
            upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
              ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (PLAYER), Mem(CheckStop), Val(3)
                storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg23), Val(1)
              endIf: 
              else: 
                clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
                storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg23), Val(0)
              endElse: 
            endUpon: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            addSlowdown: 11
            fadeOutStart: 1000, 0
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 32
  sprite: s32'null', 8
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  resetDOF: 0, 20
  resetDiffusion: 0, 20
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  sprite: s32'null', 24
endState:

            ignoreSpeedTime: 1
            hitStopTime:

            gotoLabelRequests: s32'delete'
            resetDOF: 0, 60
            resetDiffusion: 0, 60
          endIf:

                  clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL9)

                  clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP)
                  storeValue: Mem(ObjReg0), Val(0)

                    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)

                      hitStopTime: 
                    endRunOnObject:

              endElse:

          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        else: 
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'delete'
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (WALL_BREAK)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (WALL_BREAK)
      moveCameraReset: 
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 32
  sprite: s32'null', 16
  upon: (ENEMY_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
    ifTrueInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(HitPoint)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActionTime), Val(180)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActionTime), Val(300)
          storeValue: Mem(ObjReg2), Mem(ActionTime)
          modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ObjReg2), Val(180)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
        endIf: 
        else: 
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'extend'
          moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 4, 24, s32'brake'
          moveCameraTargetRotRatePitch: 0, 400, 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'brake', s32'brake'
          moveCameraTargetRotRateYaw: 0, 600, 0, 600, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'brake', s32'brake'
          moveCameraTargetPosRateX: 0, 400, 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
          moveCameraTargetPosRateY: 0, 400, 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
          moveCameraTargetPosRateZ: 0, 400, 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
          moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
          moveCameraStart: 
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'extend'
        moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 4, 24, s32'brake'
        moveCameraTargetRotRatePitch: 0, 400, 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'brake', s32'brake'
        moveCameraTargetRotRateYaw: 0, 600, 0, 600, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'brake', s32'brake'
        moveCameraTargetPosRateX: 0, 400, 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
        moveCameraTargetPosRateY: 0, 400, 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
        moveCameraTargetPosRateZ: 0, 400, 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
        moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 96, 0, 32, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
        moveCameraStart: 
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (IDLING)
    checkCurrentStateName: (PLAYER), s32'CmnActRomanCancel'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
    endIf: 
    ifNot: Mem(IsEnemyDamage)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
    endIf: 
    ifNot: Mem(IsEnemySlow)
      if: Mem(IsEnableNormalAttack)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyDistanceX), Val(540000)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  resetDOF: 0, 20
  resetDiffusion: 0, 20
  endLabel: 
  beginLabel: s32'extend'
  sprite: s32'null', 480
  beginLabel: s32'end'
  sprite: s32'null', 4
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (ENEMY_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  moveCameraStop: 32, s32'brake'
  endLabel: 
  sprite: s32'null', 28
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 28, s32'orthoone'
  beginLabel: s32'extratime'
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ObjReg0), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ObjReg0), Val(1)
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'extratime'
  endIf: 
  endLabel: 
  beginLabel: s32'delete'
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  endLabel: 
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterSlowSettings'
  ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY), Val(0)
    ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY), Val(150000)
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        slowMoveRate: 0, 0
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER), (PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY), Val(0)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosY), Val(150000)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        slowMoveRate: 0, 0
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterTrack'
  runOnObject: (STACK0)
    setPosXBetweenObject: 3, 32
    setPosYBetweenObject: 3, 32
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(-1150000)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg6), Val(1000000)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnThrowPosition_Limit'
  endRunOnObject: 
  setPosXBetweenObject: 3, 32
  setPosYBetweenObject: 3, 32
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosY), Val(90000)
    storeValue: Mem(PosY), Val(90000)
  endIf: 
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(-1300000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg6), Val(1300000)
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnThrowPosition_Limit'
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ObjReg6), (PLAYER), Mem(EnemyDistanceX)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(16), Mem(ObjReg6)
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ObjReg3), (PLAYER), Mem(EnemyDistanceY)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(9), Mem(ObjReg3)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(30)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(20)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ObjReg6), Mem(ObjReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ObjReg3), Mem(ObjReg6)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(480000)
    storeValue: Mem(ObjReg3), Val(480000)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(380000)
    storeValue: Mem(ObjReg3), Val(380000)
  endIf: 
  storeValue: Mem(ObjReg4), Val(110000)
  storeValue: Mem(ObjReg5), Val(110000)
  storeValue: Mem(ObjReg6), Mem(ObjReg3)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Val(460000), Mem(ObjReg6), Mem(ObjReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(7)
  modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(-30)
  modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg6)
  modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg6)
  ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (PLAYER), Mem(IsAir), Val(1)
    ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(IsAir), Val(1)
      storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ObjReg6), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(0)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(-4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(1), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg7), Val(6)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg7)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(-16), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(1), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg7), Val(1)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg7)
        storeValue: Mem(ObjReg4), Val(5000)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ObjReg6), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(DmgAtkAngle)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(0)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(5000)
        modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(90)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(70), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(3), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg7)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(5000)
        modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(90)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(3), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(3), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg7)
      endElse: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ObjReg6), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(DmgAtkAngle)
    ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(IsLand), Val(1)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(0)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(5000)
        modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(90)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(40), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(2), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg7)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(5000)
        modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(90)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(3), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(3), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg7)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(0)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(5000)
        modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(90)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(12), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(2), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg7)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(5000)
        modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(90)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(3), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ObjReg4), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg6), Val(3), Mem(ObjReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg5), Mem(ObjReg7)
      endElse: 
    endElse: 
  endElse: 
  moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 4, 30, s32'brake'
  ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER), (PLAYER), Mem(EnemyFrontDistance), Val(0)
    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, 54000, 2, 56, 2, 57, 0, 8, 0, 400, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
    moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, -32000, 0, 120000, 2, 58, 0, 8, 0, 400, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  endIf: 
  else: 
    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, -54000, 2, 56, 2, 57, 0, 8, 0, 400, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
    moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 32000, 0, 120000, 2, 58, 0, 8, 0, 400, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  endElse: 
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(30)
  modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(100)
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ObjReg3), (PLAYER), Mem(EnemyDistanceY)
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(0)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ObjReg3), Mem(ObjReg2)
      storeValue: Mem(ObjReg2), Mem(ObjReg3)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ObjReg2), Val(1000000)
        storeValue: Mem(ObjReg2), Val(1000000)
      endIf: 
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ObjReg2), Val(40000), Mem(ObjReg3)
      modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ObjReg3), Val(60)
      moveCameraFOV: 2, 56, 0, 8, 0, 100, 0, 16, s32'linear', s32'linear'
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnHighGuard'
  ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(DmgAtkAngleGuardForce), Val(2147483647)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(DmgAtkAngleGuardForce), Val(45)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(DmgAtkAngleGuardForce), Val(-45)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    posTypeToVar: (SELF), (DAMAGE), Val(0), Mem(ActReg2)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActReg0)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(DmgAtkAngle), Val(45)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActReg0)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(DmgAtkAngle), Val(-45)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endElse: 
endSubroutine:

  endUpon:

  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnJumpPre'
  inertiaPercent: 60
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
    upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
      whiffCancelOptionBufferTime: s32'CmnFAirDash', 3
      whiffCancelOptionBufferTime: s32'CmnBAirDash', 3
      ifNot: Mem(IsLand)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmnLandingStiffadd'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
    upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
      whiffCancelOptionBufferTime: s32'CmnFAirDash', 4
      whiffCancelOptionBufferTime: s32'CmnBAirDash', 4
      ifNot: Mem(IsLand)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmnLandingStiffadd'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
  checkLastStateName: s32'WildAssault'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    inertiaPercent: 150
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnFDash'
  checkCurrentStateEntryName: s32'CmnFDash'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    enableProximityBlock: 1
    enableBlock: 1
    enableBackDash: 1
    resetDashEasyInput: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnFDashCancel'
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(0)
      physicsXImpulse: 0, 20000
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(1)
      physicsXImpulse: 0, 20000
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(2)
      physicsXImpulse: 0, 12500
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
      setEventTrigger: (TIMER), 23
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
      setEventTrigger: (TIMER), 25
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
      setEventTrigger: (TIMER), 27
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg2), Val(0)
      upon: (TIMER)
        addInertia: 20000
        jumpToState: s32'CmnActFDashStop'
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg2), Val(1)
      upon: (TIMER)
        addInertia: 20000
        jumpToState: s32'CmnActFDashStop'
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg2), Val(2)
      upon: (TIMER)
        addInertia: 12500
        jumpToState: s32'CmnActFDashStop'
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endElse: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnFDashStop'
  enableProximityBlock: 1
  enableBlock: 1
  enableBackDash: 1
endSubroutine:

    createParticle: s32'cmn_dash_cancel', (PLAYER)

    createParticle: s32'cmn_dash_cancel2', (PLAYER)

    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(3)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    addInertia: 10000
  endUpon:

endSubroutine:

        setGravity: 0

  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnBurst'
  recoveryState: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  enableSuperArmor: 1
  superArmorArmorBreak: 1
  ignorePushback: 1
  ignoreSlowdown: 1
  suikomare: 0
  removeAllRisc: 
  IgnoreGroundFrozenMove: 1
  if: Mem(CmnCharaReg22)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg22), Val(10)
  endIf: 
  ifTrueInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg22)
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg22), Val(10)
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  checkCurrentStateEntryName: s32'CmnMaximumBurst'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    voiceLine: s16'vxxx115'
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(11)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(32)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(0)
    modifyBurstGauge: -15000
  endIf: 
  else: 
    voiceLine: s16'vxxx114'
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(11)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(41)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(28)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(1)
    modifyBurstGauge: -15000
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSBPointLimit'
  endElse: 
  warp: (SELF), (PLAYER), Val(0), Val(200000), Mem(ActReg0)
  velocityYPercentEachFrame: 95
  upon: (IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg0)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosY), Val(140000)
        velocityYPercent: 95
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg0)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'_Bakuhatsu'
      haltMomentum: 1
      zLine: 2, 5
      checkCurrentStateEntryName: s32'CmnMaximumBurst'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        createObject: s32'cmn_BurstObjGold', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        createObject: s32'cmn_BurstObjBlue', (PLAYER)
      endElse: 
      if: Mem(CmnCharaReg22)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg22), Val(10)
      endIf: 
      ifTrueInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg22)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg22), Val(10)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
        checkSignalName: s32'cmn_burst'
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL0)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(1)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg1)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'_Drop'
      defaultGravity: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg2)
      ifNot: Mem(ActReg3)
        enableSuperArmor: 0
        setStrikeInvulnerable: 0
        setThrowInvulnerable: 1
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
    landingAutoAction: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      ifNot: Mem(ActReg3)
        enableSuperArmor: 0
        damageToAir: 0
        setStrikeInvulnerable: 0
        setThrowInvulnerable: 0
      endIf: 
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(9)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          jumpToState: s32'_NEUTRAL'
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnThrowPosition_F_Wall'
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    ifNot: Mem(Dir)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg3)
        upon: (IDLING)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
          if: Mem(ActReg2)
            modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg4)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg4)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg4)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
            storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0)
          endElse: 
        endUpon: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg3)
        upon: (IDLING)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
          if: Mem(ActReg2)
            modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg4)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg4)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg4)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
            storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0)
          endElse: 
        endUpon: 
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnThrowPosition_B_Wall'
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    if: Mem(Dir)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg3)
        upon: (IDLING)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
          if: Mem(ActReg2)
            modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg4)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg4)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg4)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
            storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0)
          endElse: 
        endUpon: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg3)
        upon: (IDLING)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
          if: Mem(ActReg2)
            modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg4)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg4)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg4)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
            storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg0)
          endElse: 
        endUpon: 
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnThrowPosition_Limit'
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    if: Mem(Dir)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(-1)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
        storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
        storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
        storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
        storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnInitializeThrowBaseAndTarget'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_InitializeBase'
  createObject: s32'cmnCam_Target', (PLAYER)
  stackObject: (STACK0), (PREVIOUS)
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Mem(FuncArg0)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg6), Mem(FuncArg1)
    if: Mem(Dir)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(-1)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
        storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
        storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
        storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
        storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Mem(FuncArg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg6), Mem(FuncArg3)
    ifTrueInObject: (STACK0), Mem(Dir)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(-1)
      storeValueFromObject: (STACK0), Mem(ActReg5), (SELF), Mem(ActReg5)
      storeValueFromObject: (STACK0), Mem(ActReg6), (SELF), Mem(ActReg6)
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
        storeValueFromObject: (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), (STACK0), Mem(ActReg6)
      endIf: 
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
        storeValueFromObject: (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), (STACK0), Mem(ActReg5)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      storeValueFromObject: (STACK0), Mem(ActReg5), (SELF), Mem(ActReg5)
      storeValueFromObject: (STACK0), Mem(ActReg6), (SELF), Mem(ActReg6)
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg5)
        storeValueFromObject: (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), (STACK0), Mem(ActReg5)
      endIf: 
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg6)
        storeValueFromObject: (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), (STACK0), Mem(ActReg6)
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

        sendSignalToAction: s32'cmn_Chase_Camera', (SIGNAL0)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      sendSignalToAction: s32'cmn_Chase_Camera', (SIGNAL0)
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnCam_AirThrowPre'

    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 460000, 0, 135000, 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'

    moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
