beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_AirThrow'
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    sendValuesToObject: 2, 330, 2, 331
    createObjectWithArg: s32'cmnCam_AirThrowAction', (PLAYER)
  endIf: 
  else: 
    setMotionBlurAmount: 10
  endElse: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnCam_AirThrowAction'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnInitializeThrowBaseAndTarget', Val(-960000), Val(960000), Val(-960000), Val(960000)
    moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 23, 8, s32'accel_brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 135000, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'accel_brake'
    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 460000, 0, 135000, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosRateX: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosRateY: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosRateZ: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 200, s32'orthoone'
    resetDOF: 1, 1
    focalDistance: -1, 700, 0
    focalRegion: -1, 0, 0
    focalNearTransition: -1, 0, 0
    focalFarTransition: -1, 500, 0
    focalNearBlurSize: -1, 0, 0
    focalFarBlurSize: -1, 5, 10
    resetDiffusion: 1, 1
    setDiffusionLuminance: -1, 1400, 40
    setDiffusionThreshold: -1, 0, 40
    upon: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP)
      runOnObject: (STACK0)
        setPosXBetweenObject: 3, 32
        setPosYBetweenObject: 3, 32
      endRunOnObject: 
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_GREATER), (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), Val(960000)
        runOnObject: (STACK0)
          storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Val(960000)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER), (STACK0), Mem(PosXRaw), Val(-960000)
        runOnObject: (STACK0)
          storeValue: Mem(PosXRaw), Val(-960000)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(SentToObject0), Val(0)
        warp: (STACK0), (PLAYER), Val(0), Val(0), Val(8)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        warp: (STACK0), (PLAYER), Val(0), Val(0), Mem(SentToObject1)
      endElse: 
      checkCurrentStateName: (PLAYER), s32'AirThrowExe'
      ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL0)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL0)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 180
  endLabel: 
  beginLabel: s32'end'
  sprite: s32'null', 20
  moveCameraStop: 20, s32'brake'
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 20, s32'orthoone'
  resetDOF: 0, 20
  resetDiffusion: 0, 20
  moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 23, 20, s32'accel_brake'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraFOV: 0, 65, 0, 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_Initialize'
  runOnObject: (PLAYER)
    slowdownEndOnHit: 1
  endRunOnObject: 
  ignoreSlowdown: 1
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_cam_delete_on_rc'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_cam_delete_on_wsb'
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_InitializeBase'
  linkCommonPawn: 
  if: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'accel_brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'linear'
    moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'brake'
  endIf: 
  else: 
    moveCameraReset: 
    resetCamera: 
  endElse: 
  moveCameraBasePosObject: (SELF)
  sendSignalToAction: s32'cmnHiCounterCamera', (SIGNAL9)
  ignoreSlowdown: 1
  createObject: s32'cmnCam_Singleton', (PLAYER)
  upon: (ACTION_END)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_ClearCamInterrupt'
    sendSignalToAction: s32'cmnCam_Singleton', (SIGNAL0)
    deactivateObjectById: (STACK0)
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'DeleteCamera'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_ClearCamInterrupt'
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
      deactivateObjectById: (STACK0)
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (WALL_BREAK)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_ClearCamInterrupt'
    deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    deactivateObjectById: (STACK0)
    if: Mem(BattleDoing)
      createObject: s32'cmnCam_ReturnToDefault', (PLAYER)
    endIf: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
  endUpon: 
  upon: (WALL)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_ClearCamInterrupt'
    deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    deactivateObjectById: (STACK0)
    createObject: s32'cmnCam_ReturnToDefault', (PLAYER)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
  endUpon: 
  upon: (GUARD)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_ClearCamInterrupt'
    deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    deactivateObjectById: (STACK0)
    createObject: s32'cmnCam_ReturnToDefault', (PLAYER)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
  endUpon: 
  upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_ClearCamInterrupt'
    deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    deactivateObjectById: (STACK0)
    createObject: s32'cmnCam_ReturnToDefault', (PLAYER)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
  endUpon: 
  upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_CommonCameraEnd'
    if: Mem(BattleDoing)
      ifNot: Mem(IsSomebodysCutScene)
        resetDOF: 0, 20
        resetDiffusion: 0, 20
        resetSaturation: 0, 20
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  if: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    moveCameraFOV: 0, 65, 0, 0, 0, 500, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
    resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  endIf: 
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_cam_delete_on_rc'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterSlowSettings'
  moveCameraStart: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnCam_FinishTimeOut'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    ignoreFinishStop: 1
    ignoreSlowdown: 1
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 130
  sprite: s32'null', 20
  ifNot: Mem(IsSomebodysCutScene)
    focalDistance: 700, 0, 0
    focalRegion: 0, 0, 0
    focalNearTransition: 0, 0, 0
    focalFarTransition: 500, 0, 0
    focalNearBlurSize: 0, 0, 0
    focalFarBlurSize: 40, 0, 0
    resetDOF: 0, 20
    resetSaturation: 0, 20
    resetDiffusion: 0, 20
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
    cinesco: 0
  endIf: 
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  ifNot: Mem(IsSomebodysCutScene)
    hideUI: 0
  endIf: 
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
  removeGlareEffect: 0, 0
  removeGlareEffect: 0, 1
  removeGlareEffect: 0, 2
  removeGlareEffect: 0, 3
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnCam_ReturnToDefault'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    setPosXBetweenObject: 3, 32
    moveCameraBasePosObject: (SELF)
    moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 23, 30, s32'accel_brake'
    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 460000, 0, 135000, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'accel', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 135000, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraFOV: 0, 65, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraStop: 30, s32'brake'
    moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'linear'
    moveCameraTrackUp: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
    ifNot: Mem(BattleDoing)
      resetDOF: 0, 20
      resetDiffusion: 0, 20
      resetSaturation: 0, 20
      cinesco: 0
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  sprite: s32'null', 29
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthodefault', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_InitializeTarget'
  linkCommonPawn: 
  runOnObject: (PLAYER)
  endRunOnObject: 
  ignoreSlowdown: 1
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_ClearCamInterrupt'
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (WALL_BREAK)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (WALL)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (ACTION_END)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_EXIT)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (ENEMY_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
  sendSignalToAction: s32'cmnCam_Singleton', (SIGNAL0)
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCameraSettings'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg3), Val(0)
    sendSignalToAction: s32'cmnCam_Singleton', (SIGNAL1)
    ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
      moveCameraReset: 
      resetCamera: 
      deactivateObjectByNameAll: s32'cmnHiCounterCamera'
    endIf: 
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      resetMotionBlurAmount: 
      deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      resetMotionBlurAmount: 
      deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
    endRunOnObject: 
    if: Mem(IsTo3)
      isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
          resetMotionBlurAmount: 
          deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
          resetMotionBlurAmount: 
          deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
          resetMotionBlurAmount: 
          deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
          resetMotionBlurAmount: 
          deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg3), Val(1)
    cinesco: 0
    hideUI: 0
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
    resetDOF: 0, 40
    resetSaturation: 0, 20
    resetDiffusion: 0, 40
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnCam_Singleton'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    storeValue: Mem(ObjReg0), Val(0)
    moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthozero', 0, 500, s32'orthoone'
    deactivateObjectByNameExceptSelf: s32'cmnCam_Singleton'
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnCam_Singleton'
    endRunOnObject: 
    upon: (SIGNAL0)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL0)
      storeValue: Mem(ObjReg0), Val(1)
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL1)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL1)
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
      sendSignalName: 2, s32'DeleteCamera', 0
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (ON_DELETE)
      resetMotionBlurAmount: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (ON_DELETE)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (ON_DELETE)
      if: Mem(ObjReg0)
        moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthodefault', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
      endIf: 
      else: 
        sendSignalName: 2, s32'DeleteCamera', 0
      endElse: 
      resetMotionBlurAmount: 
    endUpon: 
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 500
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmnCam_RC'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_InitializeBase'
    createObject: s32'cmnCam_RC_Target', (PLAYER)
    stackObject: (STACK0), (PREVIOUS)
    setPosXBetweenObject: 3, 32
    setPosYBetweenObject: 3, 32
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(-1250000)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg6), Val(1250000)
    moveCameraBasePosObject: (SELF)
    moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 23, 14, s32'accel_brake'
    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 150000, 0, 135000, 0, 14, 0, 14, 0, 0, s32'accel', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 135000, 0, 14, 0, 14, 0, 0, s32'accel', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 14, 0, 1, 0, 14, s32'accel', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 14, 0, 1, 0, 14, s32'accel', s32'brake'
    moveCameraFOV: 0, 63, 0, 14, 0, 0, 0, 14, s32'accel', s32'brake'
    setMotionBlurAmount: 300
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
    moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 14
  cameraShakeEX: s32'shake_temae', 100, 0, 10, 0, s32'brake'
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmnCam_RC_Target'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 500
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_cam_delete_on_rc'
  upon: (AFTER_EXIT)
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      checkCurrentStateName: (PLAYER), s32'CmnActRomanCancel'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmnCam_ClearCamInterrupt'
        deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
        deactivateObjectById: (STACK0)
        ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
          createObject: s32'cmnCam_ReturnToDefault', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_cam_delete_on_wsb'
  upon: (WALL_BREAK)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (WALL_BREAK)
    deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    moveCameraReset: 
    moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthozero', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_cam_delete_on_finish'
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (WALL_BREAK)
  deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
  moveCameraReset: 
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthozero', 0, 1, s32'orthoone'
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_vertical_offset'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(-3)
    pushScreenOffset: 0, -240000, 0, 0
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(-2)
    pushScreenOffset: 0, -160000, 0, 0
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(-1)
    pushScreenOffset: 0, -80000, 0, 0
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
    pushScreenOffset: 0, 80000, 0, 0
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
    pushScreenOffset: 0, 160000, 0, 0
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)
    pushScreenOffset: 0, 240000, 0, 0
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_motionblur'
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 50
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 80
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 100
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(4)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 150
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(5)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 200
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(6)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 300
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(7)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 400
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(8)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 500
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(9)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 700
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(10)
      setMotionBlurAmount: 1000
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

    createObjectWithArg: s32'cmnBlurTimeout', (PLAYER)
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnBlurTimeout'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
    ignoreSlowdown: 1
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(SentToObject1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_motionblur', Mem(SentToObject0), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 180
endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnMutekiRC'
  enableRomanCancelMove: 0
  if: Mem(FuncArg0)
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      if: Mem(IsWorldStopperOther)
        enableRomanCancelMove: 0
      endIf: 
      else: 
        ifTrueInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PlayerDamageOrGuard)
          enableRomanCancelMove: 1
        endIf: 
        else: 
          checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), s32'CmnActBurst'
          if: Mem(Tmp)
            ifTrueInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(ActReg4)
              enableRomanCancelMove: 1
            endIf: 
            else: 
              enableRomanCancelMove: 0
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            enableRomanCancelMove: 0
          endElse: 
        endElse: 
      endElse: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (WALL_BREAK)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      enableRomanCancelMove: 0
    endUpon: 
    slowdownEndOnHit: 1
  endIf: 
  else: 
    doNotBeginCancel: 1
  endElse: 
endSubroutine:

      blockstunAmount: 18
      riscGain: 25
      pushbackX: 100
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (HIT)

      clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_PRIVATE)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (COUNTER_HIT)

      checkMoveFlag: (ENEMY_IN_HITSTUN)

        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(1)
      endIf:

      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(0)
      endIf: 
      checkCurrentStateName: (DEFENDER), s32'CmnActHajikareCrouch'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(0)
      endIf: 
      checkCurrentStateName: (DEFENDER), s32'CmnActHajikareAir'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(0)
      endIf: 
      ifNot: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(1)
      endIf: 
      ifNotInObject: (DEFENDER), Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(1)
      endIf: 
      ifNot: Mem(ActReg5)
        battleStats: s32'GiveDustCounter', 0, 1

          battleStats: s32'SufferDustCounter', 0, 1
        endRunOnObject: 
        disableWallBreak: 1
        counterDisableWallBreak: 1
        forceWallBreak: 0
        hitStop: 45
        shortHitstop: 0
        disableHitstop: 0
        slowHitstop: 1, 1
        hitAirPushbackX: 0, 50000
        hitAirPushbackY: 0, 75000
        riscConsumeStarter: 5
        setProration: 100
        forcedComboScaleCount: 0
        pushbackX: 200
        groundHitEffect: (TAILSPIN)
        airHitEffect: (TAILSPIN)
        attackFrontDirection: 0
        wallBounceCount: 0
        noGravityScaling: 0

        dustInvulnTime: 1

              checkIfMoveExists: s32'HomingJump'

                addPdChain: s32'HomingJump'
              endIf:

                  runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
                    hitStopTime: 
                  endRunOnObject: 
                endIf: 
                checkLastDamageActionNameAndAirStun: 34, s32'NmlAtk5E'
                if: Mem(Tmp)
                  runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
                    hitStopTime: 
                  endRunOnObject:

                  clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)

                    removePDChain: s32'HomingJump'
                    invulnForce: 0

              focalFarTransition: -1, 500, 0
              focalNearBlurSize: -1, 0, 0
              focalFarBlurSize: -1, 40, 10

              moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 25, 10, s32'linear'
              moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, 0, 2, 45, 2, 46, 0, 10, 0, 400, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
              moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 47, 0, 10, 0, 400, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'

              moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthozero', 0, 0, s32'orthodefault'

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Dust_Kirimomi_Blend'
  spriteSlowParam: 1, 1, 0, 0, 45, 1000
  spriteSlowParamFinishStop: 1, 1, 0, 0, 120, 1000
  slowMoveRate: 0, 500
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterSlowSettings'
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg18), Val(1)
  upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg18), Val(0)
  endUpon: 
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(600)
  upon: (IDLING)
    if: Mem(IsLastDamageDustAttack)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1000)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
      endIf: 
      modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(200)
      spriteBlendNext: 2, 45, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(2)
        cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Blow_Spin'
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(35)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
        cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Blow_Spin'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    if: Mem(IsLastDamageDustAttack)
      ifNot: Mem(CheckStop)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg3), Val(0)
          pushVelocityX: 
          pushVelocityY: 
          haltMomentum: 1
          addVelocityX: 0, -10000
          addVelocityY: 0, 10000
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg3), Val(14)
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(10)
            storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1250)
            storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(1250)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1750)
            storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(2500)
          endElse: 
          modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActionTime)
          modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActionTime)
          addPositionX: 2, 46
          addPositionY: 2, 47
        endIf: 
        else: 
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
          checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), s32'HomingJump'
          if: Mem(Tmp)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            physicsXImpulse: 0, -50000
            physicsYImpulse: 0, 75000
            velocityXPercent: 40
            velocityYPercent: 5
            setGravity: 3000
          endElse: 
        endElse: 
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg3), Val(1)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Dust_HomingJump'
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthozero', 0, 0, s32'orthozero'
  pauseTimer: 1
  invulnForce: 1
  runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    invulnForce: 1
  endRunOnObject: 
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg18), Val(1)
  if: Mem(Afro)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_AfroCS'
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg7), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  battleStats: s32'DustHoming', 0, 1
  battleStats: s32'DustHomingJump', 0, 1
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(1)
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(1)
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(1)
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(1)
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(1)
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(1)
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  disableWall: 1
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(16)
      ifNot: Mem(Dir)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosX), Val(500000)
          setPositionXInBattle: 500000
        endIf:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Dust_HomingJump_Loop'
  haltMomentum: 1
  physicsXImpulse: 0, 2500
  physicsYImpulse: 0, 5000
  setGravity: 500
  runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    haltMomentum: 1
    setGravity: 750
  endRunOnObject: 
  enableNormals: 1
  enableSpecials: 1
  enableDoubleJump: 1
  enableAirForwardDash: 1
  enableAirBackDash: 1
  enableProximityBlock: 1
  enableBlock: 1
  addDoubleJumpCount: 1
  addAirDashCount: 1
  disableWall: 1
  landingHeight: -10000000
  upon: (PRE_FRAME_STEP)
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      landingHeight: -10000000
      keepAirDamageActionUpper: 1
    endRunOnObject: 
  endUpon: 
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(1)
  storeValueFromObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg5), (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
  ifNot: Mem(Dir)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  else: 
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(-1)
  endElse: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(69)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(70)
      jumpToState: s32'DebugSkillEx'
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

  upon: (RECEIVE_ATTACK)
    recoveryState: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_PRE_CONTROL)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_PRE_CONTROL)
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_Chase_Camera'
    callPrivateFunction: s32'DustSpeedCtrl', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0
    haltMomentum: 1
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      haltMomentum: 1
    endRunOnObject: 
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmn_Dust_SpeedLine'
    slowdownEndOnHit: 1
    enableRomanCancelMove: 0
    enableGatlings: 0
    enableWhiffCancel: 0
    callPrivateFunction: s32'ClearPastSenkoInputTime', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0
    addTensionBalance: 0, 5000
    addTensionBalance: 0, 25000
    forcePositiveBonus: 1
    battleStats: s32'DustAtkEndOK', 0, 1
    superFreeze: 0, 119, 30, 30
    upon: (SUPERFREEZE)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
      cameraShakeEX: s32'Vertical', 2500, 0, 10, 0, s32'linear'
      upon: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)
        ifNot: Mem(BattleDoing)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
            clearRegisteredUponCode: (SUPERFREEZE)
            superFreeze: 0, 119, 1, 1
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        if: Mem(BattleDoing)
          runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
            addPositionX: 0, -500
            addPositionY: 0, -800
          endRunOnObject: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
          ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(0)
            requestForceWallBreakDust: 2, 1
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(0)
            requestForceWallBreakDust: 1, 1
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
          checkWallBreakOrigin: 
          storeValueFromObject: (PLAYER), Mem(ActReg1), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosX)
          modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
          ifNot: Mem(Dir)
            modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-2500000)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg1), Val(2500000)
          endElse: 
          storeValueFromObject: (PLAYER), Mem(ActReg2), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY)
          modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg2), Val(4000000)
          requestAddPosNoLinkAllObject: 2, 46, 2, 47, 0, 0
          requestAddPosNoLinkAllParticle: 2, 46, 2, 47, 0, 0
          createObject: s32'cmn_Dust_Finish_Camera', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(29)
          runOnObject: (PLAYER)
            jumpToState: s32'WorldSideBreak_Master_DS'
          endRunOnObject: 
          runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'WorldSideBreak_Slave_DS'
          endRunOnObject: 
          ifNotInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(HitPoint)
            runOnObject: (PLAYER)
              ignoreFinishStop: 1
            endRunOnObject: 
            runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
              ignoreFinishStop: 1
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
    attackVoiceLine: 2, 0
    createObject: s32'cmn_wsb_dust_in', (PLAYER)
  endUpon: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(48)
    haltMomentum: 1
    upon: (IDLING)
      pauseSprite: 1
      checkInput: (INPUT_ANY_DOWN)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        setPositionY: 4750005
        physicsYImpulse: 0, -1
      endIf: 
      ifNot: Mem(ActReg7)
        checkInput: 2
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg7), Val(1)
        endIf: 
        checkInput: 11
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg7), Val(2)
        endIf: 
        checkInput: 20
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg7), Val(3)
        endIf: 
        checkInput: 29
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg7), Val(4)
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg7), Val(-1)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg7), Val(0)
          grabOrRelease: 
          attackCollisionForceExpand: 1
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Dust_End_Master'
  dustEndLockParamClear: 0, 1500000

  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg20), Val(0)
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg21), Val(0)

  upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    disableWall: 0
    wallBreakSceneEnd:

    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)

      enemyUniqueEffectOff: 
    endRunOnObject:

      isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)

        endRunOnObject:

        requestForceWallBreakDust: 2, 0
        faceRight: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(0)

        faceLeft: 
      endIf:

      physicsXImpulse: 0, 52500
      physicsYImpulse: 0, -40000
      setGravity: 1500
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
      resetCamera: 
      checkWallBreakOrigin:

        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-2000000)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(0)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg1), Val(2000000)
      endIf:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Dust_End_Slave'
  dustEndLockParamClear: 0, 1500000
  playerActionInitializeByCategory: 61, 0
  enableRomanCancelMove: 0
  invulnForce: 1
  landingAutoAction: 0
  pauseTimer: 1
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(0)
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg20), Val(0)
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg21), Val(0)
  callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_dll_Damage', Val(11), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  superFreeze: 0, 119, 1, 1
  disableWall: 1
  upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    disableWall: 0
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(WSBPoint), Val(0)
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      enemyUniqueEffectOff: 
    endRunOnObject: 
    if: Mem(IsTo3)
      isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg5), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      callPrivateFunction: s32'MemberChangeInValid', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), s32'WorldSideBreak_Master_DF'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(0)
          storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(CmnCharaReg4), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg4)
          ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(0)
            faceRight: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(CmnCharaReg4), Val(0)
            faceLeft: 
          endIf: 
          flipDirection: 
          setNoCollision: 0
          moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          addPositionX: 0, -350000
          addPositionY: 0, 350000
          physicsXImpulse: 0, -50000
          physicsYImpulse: 0, -40000
          createObject: s32'cmn_wsb_dust_in_miss', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(1)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setNoCollision: 1
          setGravity: 2000
          landingAutoAction: 0
          landingAutoEffect: 0
          upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
            ifNot: Mem(HitPoint)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
            endElse: 
            physicsXImpulse: 0, -20000
            velocityXPercentEachFrame: 95
            upon: (IDLING)
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(22)
                clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
                physicsXImpulse: 0, 0
              endIf: 
            endUpon: 
            effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
          endUpon: 
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginState: s32'cmn_Dust_Speed'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifTrueInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(IsLastDamageDustAttack)
        storeValueFromObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedX), (PLAYER), Mem(SpeedX)
        storeValueFromObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY), (PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY)
        storeValueFromObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(Gravity), (PLAYER), Mem(Gravity)
        ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(30)
          runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
            velocityXPercent: -100
            velocityYPercent: 80
            gravityPercent: 150
            addDepth: 0, -50000
          endRunOnObject: 
        endIf: 
        else: 
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(35)
            runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
              velocityXPercent: -90
              velocityYPercent: 85
              gravityPercent: 100
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(45)
              runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
                velocityXPercent: -80
                velocityYPercent: 70
                gravityPercent: 100
                setDepth: -125000
              endRunOnObject: 
            endIf: 
            else: 
              ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(49)
                runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
                  velocityXPercent: 5
                  velocityYPercent: 50
                  addDepth: 0, 25000
                endRunOnObject: 
              endIf: 
              else: 
                runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
                  velocityXPercent: -100
                  velocityYPercent: 100
                  addVelocityY: 0, 2500
                  setDepth: 0
                endRunOnObject: 
                deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
              endElse: 
            endElse: 
          endElse: 
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      ifNotInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(IsLastDamageDustAttack)
        deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 100
endState:

      setAcceleration: 1000
    endIf:

      setAcceleration: 0

endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnAtkTemplNage__EnemyCell'
  checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'ThrowExe'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    spriteByDamageEx: s32'LandThrow'
    enemyGrabSprite: 22
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyFrontDistance), Val(0)
      exPointFReset: (PLAYER), 157500, 0
    endIf: 
    else: 
      exPointFReset: (PLAYER), -157500, 0
    endElse: 
    setGripPosition: (EX_POINT_F), (PLAYER), 0
  endIf: 
  checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'AirThrowExe'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    spriteByDamageEx: s32'AirThrow'
    enemyGrabSprite: 23
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyFrontDistance), Val(0)
      exPointFReset: (PLAYER), 157500, 0
    endIf: 
    else: 
      exPointFReset: (PLAYER), -157500, 0
    endElse: 
    setGripPosition: (EX_POINT_F), (PLAYER), 0
    createObject: s32'cmnCam_AirThrowPre', (PLAYER)
  endIf: 
  spriteTimeAdd: 8
  zLine: 3, 5
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnAtkTemplNageFinish'
  riscConsume: 10
  prorationTandan: 1
  forcedComboScaleCount: 25
  wallBreakDamageNoUpdate: 0
  noExtraGravity: 1
  counterHitType: (NO_COUNTER)
  enableRomanCancelMove: 1
  dontAddComboCount: 0
  attackIgnoreOutPower: 0
  enableExRomanCancel: 0
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(0)
  callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_dll_Damage', Val(10), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  ifNot: Mem(FuncArg0)
    riscConsume: 25
    setForcedProration: 50
    addTension: 200
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnNageWSBPoint'
    sendSignalToAction: s32'cmnCam_AirThrowAction', (SIGNAL0)
  endIf: 
  if: Mem(FuncArg1)
    runOnObject: (DEFENDER)
      modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(WSBPoint), Val(-500)
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  if: Mem(AdjustmentForScript0)
    exPointFReset: (PLAYER_LAND), 0, -1000000
    setGripPosition: (EX_POINT_F), (PLAYER), 0
  endIf: 
  deleteMoveForceDisableFlag: 1073741824
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg31), Val(0)
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_vsJKO_ElysionDriver'
  swapMeshSet: s32'headonly'
  linkBone: 0
  faceOpponent: 
  reverseDisplay: 1
  zLine: 0, 5
  upon: (PRE_DRAW)
    moveToObject: (LOCKED)
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_maincheck'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
    upon: (PRE_HIT_COLLISION)
      ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PRE_HIT_COLLISION)
        recoveryState: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
    ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
      returnValue: 0, 1
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_subcheck'
  ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(IsSubMember1Self)
    returnValue: 0, 1
  endIf: 
  ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(IsSubMember2Self)
    returnValue: 0, 2
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_lockcheck'
  upon: (PLAYER_AFTER_EXECUTE_DAMAGE)
    ifTrueInObject: (DEFENDER), Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_AFTER_EXECUTE_DAMAGE)
      callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_changecheck', Val(2), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
      pushCollisionOnPlayersOnly: 1
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_leavecheck'
  checkMoveFlag: 133
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    checkMoveFlag: (IS_SUB_PLAYER)
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      returnValue: 0, 1
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_changecheck'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg29), Val(0)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg29), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg29), Val(2)
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Hizakuzure'
  upon: (IDLING)
    if: Mem(BattleDoing)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(51)
        landingEffect: 100, 1, 0
        crashSfx: 0, 100
        setCrouch: 1
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        crashSfx: 1, 100
        landingEffect: 100, 1, 0
        jumpToState: s32'CmnActFDownLoop'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifNot: Mem(BattleDoing)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'ko'
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(46)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript3), Val(1)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'ko'
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

    clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_PRIVATE)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkTemplFloatDamage'
    floatHead: 1
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkTemplFloatDamageBody'
  upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_PRIVATE)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_PRIVATE)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkTemplFloatDamage'
    floatBody: 1
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_FloatDamage'
  haltMomentum: 1
  if: Mem(IsFloatDmgHead)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(1)
        physicsXImpulse: 0, -15000
        velocityXPercentEachFrame: 90
        physicsYImpulse: 0, 20000
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(3)
        physicsYImpulse: 0, 7500
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(7)
        physicsYImpulse: 0, 2500
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(13)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
        velocityXPercentEachFrame: 80
        physicsYImpulse: 0, 0
        setGravity: 4000
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
  if: Mem(IsFloatDmgBody)
    physicsXImpulse: 0, -20000
    velocityXPercentEachFrame: 80
    setGravity: 1000
    checkLastAttackHitStateName: 3, s32'NmlAtk5E'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      upon: (FALL_SPEED)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
        ignoreSpeedTime: 1
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
    createArgScale: 0, 750
    createParticleWithArg2: s32'bg_down_default', (BACK_05_BODY)
    velocityXPercentEachFrame: 85
    if: Mem(IsFloatDmgHead)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'head_landing'
      storeValue: Mem(StunTime), Val(14)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
      upon: (IDLING)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(8)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          enableBlock: 1
          enableInvalidCombo: 1
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
    if: Mem(IsFloatDmgBody)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'body_landing'
      storeValue: Mem(StunTime), Val(17)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
      upon: (IDLING)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(7)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          enableBlock: 1
          enableInvalidCombo: 1
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkTemplNmlAtkAir'
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(SpeedX), Val(0)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(SpeedX), Val(4), Mem(CmnCharaActReg5)
      modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CmnCharaActReg3), Mem(CmnCharaActReg5)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(SpeedY), Val(0)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(SpeedY), Val(2), Mem(CmnCharaActReg5)
      modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CmnCharaActReg4), Mem(CmnCharaActReg5)
    endIf: 
    hitAirPushbackX: 2, 346
    hitAirPushbackY: 2, 347
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

    guardGravity: 1250
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
    airGuardPushbackX: 2500
    airGuardPushbackY: 15000
    guardGravity: 1500
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)
    airGuardPushbackX: 2500
    airGuardPushbackY: 10000
    guardGravity: 2000
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(4)
    airGuardPushbackX: 2500
    airGuardPushbackY: 15000
    guardGravity: 2000
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(5)
    airGuardPushbackX: 2500
    airGuardPushbackY: 20000
    guardGravity: 2000
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(6)
    airGuardPushbackX: 2500
    airGuardPushbackY: 5000
    guardGravity: 1500
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(7)
    airGuardPushbackX: 25000
    airGuardPushbackY: 5000
    guardGravity: 1500
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(8)
    airGuardPushbackX: 0
    airGuardPushbackY: 20000
    guardGravity: 1500
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Frozen'
  setLightColor: -11505540
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      createObject: s32'cmn_FrozenEff1', (CHEST_3D)
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (TOUCH_GROUND)
    createObject: s32'cmn_FrozenEff2', (PLAYER_LAND)
  endUpon: 
  upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    ifNotInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg30)
      sendSignalToAction: s32'cmn_FrozenEff1', (SIGNAL0)
      runOnObject: (FROZEN_MASTER)
        exPointFResetObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), (PLAYER), 0, 0
        createObject: s32'cmn_FrozenEnd_Atk', (EX_POINT_F)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_GroundFrozen'
  if: Mem(IsMainPlayerSelf)
    runOnObject: (GROUND_FROZEN_MASTER)
      sendSignalToAction: s32'DZY_SAKANALAND_obj', (SIGNAL0)
      sendSignalToAction: s32'LandFrozen_End', (SIGNAL0)
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    invulnForce: 1
    jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActQuickDown'
  endElse: 
  upon: (IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(2)
      jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActQuickDown'
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    linkParticle: s32'cmn_ice_damage02'
    linkObjPosition: 3
    ignoreSlowdown: 1
    reverseDisplay: 1
    upon: (AFTER_EXIT)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_EXIT)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL0)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'

      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL0)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_EXIT)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL0)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
    endUpon: 
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnWSB_Effect_NoStop_or_Delete', Val(0), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnWSB_Effect_Angle', Val(0), Val(1), Val(0), Val(0)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Settings'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
  commonSE: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Impact_Frozen'
  commonSE: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Impact_Frozen'
  endLabel: 
  beginLabel: s32'end'
  sprite: s32'null', 60
  linkParticle: s32'cmn_ice_damage02_end'
  linkObjPosition: 0
  commonSE: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Impact_FrozenBreak'
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FrozenEff2'

    linkParticle: s32'cmn_ice_damage01'
    linkObjPosition: 3
    ignoreSlowdown: 1
    reverseDisplay: 1
    upon: (SIGNAL0)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL0)

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWorldSideBreak_Position'
  runOnObject: (PLAYER)
    setNoCollision: 0
    landingAutoAction: 0
  endRunOnObject: 
  calcDistanceEx: 0, 3, 100, 32, 100
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(Tmp), Val(500000)
    if: Mem(SentToObject0)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaActReg0), Val(-500000)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Val(-1), Mem(EnemyDiffY), Mem(CmnCharaActReg1)
    calcDistanceEx: 0, 3, 100, 32, 100
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(Tmp), Val(750000)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaActReg0), Val(-750000)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Val(-1), Mem(EnemyDistanceX), Mem(CmnCharaActReg0)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endElse: 
  endElse: 
  ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(IsLand)
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      moveToPosType: 32, 123
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      moveToPosType: 32, 100
    endRunOnObject: 
  endElse: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(3)
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaActReg0), Val(2)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(CmnCharaActReg0), Val(17), Mem(CmnCharaActReg2)
      modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaActReg2), Val(10)
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(1)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(CmnCharaActReg0), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(-1)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(CmnCharaActReg0), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  runOnObject: (PLAYER)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(CmnCharaActReg0)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(PosY), Mem(CmnCharaActReg1)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(PosZ), Mem(CmnCharaActReg2)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(AngleY), Mem(CmnCharaActReg7)
  endRunOnObject: 
  checkStageName: s16'Station_PL'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(0)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(3)
        ifOperationInObject: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaActReg7), Val(0)
          runOnObject: (PLAYER)
            modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(AngleY), Mem(CmnCharaActReg7)
          endRunOnObject: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  runOnObject: (PLAYER)
    enableRomanCancel: 0
  endRunOnObject: 
  runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    enableBurst: 0
  endRunOnObject: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWorldSideBreak_Type'
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(2184), Mem(ActReg2)
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg3), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActReg4)
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg5), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(WSBPattern)
  ifNot: Mem(ActReg5)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(1)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActReg4), Val(250000)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActReg4), Val(0)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActReg4), Val(250000)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(2)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(3)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActReg4), Val(250000)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(4)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActReg4), Val(250000)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(4)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(0)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
  if: Mem(ReturnValue)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(5)
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(ActReg1)
    debugLogForScript: s32'cmnWSB_Type', 2, 46
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWorldSideBreak_LandingHeight'
  runOnObject: (PLAYER)
    checkCeilingCollision: 0
  endRunOnObject: 
  runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    checkCeilingCollision: 0
  endRunOnObject: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(495)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(505)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        landingHeight: -1092000
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        landingHeight: -1092000
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(995)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(1005)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        landingHeight: -2184000
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        landingHeight: -2184000
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(1495)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(1505)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        landingHeight: -3276000
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        landingHeight: -3276000
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(1995)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(WSBNextHeight), Val(2005)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        landingHeight: -4368000
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        landingHeight: -4368000
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
  endIf:

        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(3)
          runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
            createObject: s32'cmnWSB_FinishCamera_3', (PLAYER)
          endRunOnObject: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(60)
        superFreeze: 0, 119, 1, 1
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(75)
        runOnObject: (PLAYER)
          ignoreFinishStop: 1
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(59)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          ignoreFinishStop: 1
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWinActionWait'
  invulnForce: 1
  faceOpponent: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  physicsYImpulse: 0, -10000
  setGravity: 2500
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(0)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(3)
      physicsYImpulse: 0, -5000000
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  zLine: 0, 5
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnWorldSideBreak_LH_Self'
  upon: (AFTER_EXIT)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWorldSideBreak_LH_Self'
  endUpon: 
  upon: (IDLING)
    ifNot: Mem(SpeedY)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
      enableDemo: 1
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  landingAutoAction: 0
  landingAutoEffect: 0
  upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (TOUCH_GROUND)
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
    enableDemo: 1
  endUpon: 
  setRawPositionXInBattle: 0
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(6)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(1500)
      addPositionX: 0, -3800000
      setDepth: -1000000
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(4500)
      addPositionX: 0, -9600000
      setDepth: -4500000
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(8000)
      addPositionX: 0, -16500000
      setDepth: -8000000
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(3)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(4500)
      addPositionX: 0, -10350000
      setDepth: -16250000
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(21000)
      addPositionX: 0, -41600000
      setDepth: -70250000
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

  endIf:

beginState: s32'cmnWSB_FinishCamera'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
    linkCommonPawn: 
    ignoreZLine: 1
    hideUI: 1
    cinesco: 1
    flipDirection: 
    resetSaturation: 1, 1
    setPostProcessSaturation: -1, 800, 40
    resetDiffusion: 1, 1
    setDiffusionLuminance: -1, 1400, 50
    setDiffusionThreshold: -1, 0, 50
    resetDOF: 1, 1
    focalDistance: -1, 700, 0
    focalRegion: -1, 0, 0
    focalNearTransition: -1, 0, 0
    focalFarTransition: -1, 500, 0
    focalNearBlurSize: -1, 0, 0
    focalFarBlurSize: -1, 10, 10
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
    createGlareEffect: 1
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Mem(Tmp)
    setGlareColor: 2, 45, 0, 127, 0, 255, 0, 255, 0, 255
    setGlareScale: 2, 45, 0, 1200, 0, 1200
    ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(Dir)
      setGlareOffset: 2, 45, 0, -300000, 0, -300000
    endIf: 
    else: 
      setGlareOffset: 2, 45, 0, 300000, 0, -300000
    endElse: 
    setEventTrigger: (TIMER), 72
    upon: (TIMER)
      resetDOF: 0, 40
      resetSaturation: 0, 20
      resetDiffusion: 0, 40
      removeGlareEffect: 2, 45
    endUpon: 
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        zLine: 0, 5
      endRunOnObject: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  resetCamera: 
  moveCameraReset: 
  moveCameraBasePosObject: (SELF)
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_finish', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_finish', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 300, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 3, 0, s32'brake'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 135000, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, -10000, 0, -15000, 0, 30, 0, 30, 0, 60, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraFOV: 0, 80, 0, 60, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 100000, 0, 135000, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraStart: 
  sprite: s32'null', 70
  sprite: s32'null', 10
  moveCameraTargetCameraOffBlend: 0, s32'linear'
  moveCameraBasePosObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
  moveCameraPos: 0, 0, 0, 460000, 0, 135000, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraFOV: 0, 65, 0, 0, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'

endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWorldSideBreak_Action_Master'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      jumpToState: s32'WSB_Master_Slide'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      jumpToState: s32'WSB_Master_Up'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      jumpToState: s32'WSB_Master_Down'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(4)
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      jumpToState: s32'WSB_Master_Bound'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(5)
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      jumpToState: s32'WSB_Master_Slide'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWorldSideBreak_Action_Slave'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'WSB_Slave_Slide'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'WSB_Slave_Up'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'WSB_Slave_Down'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(4)
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'WSB_Slave_Bound'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(5)
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'WSB_Slave_Bound'
    endRunOnObject: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Action_Default'
  playerActionInitializeByCategory: 61, 0
  invulnForce: 1
  enableRomanCancelMove: 0
  haltMomentum: 1
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  if: Mem(IsCPU)
    moveRewriteMode: 1
    addMove: s32'WSB_Master_Wait'
      addMoveFlag: 120
      removeMoveFlag: (NONE)
    endMove: 
  endIf: 
  upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnWorldSideBreakObj'
    setDepth: 0
    setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg7), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg3), Val(0)
    isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg3), Val(0)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
    isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
        storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg3), Val(0)
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
    if: Mem(IsTo3)
      isObjectActive: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg3), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      isObjectActive: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
          storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg3), Val(0)
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    storeValue: Mem(WSBPoint), Val(0)
    moveRewriteMode: 1
    addMove: s32'WSB_Master_Wait'
      addMoveFlag: 120
      removeMoveFlag: (NONE)
    endMove: 
    deactivateObjectByName: s32'cmnWSBDummy'
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg20), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg21), Val(0)
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_dll_Damage', Val(11), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  endUpon: 
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Action_LandingHeight'
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Action_Master_Default'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(6)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(4500)
      setAngleY: 35000
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(8000)
      setAngleY: 35000
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(3)
    setAngleY: 70000
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(0)
    faceRight: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(0)
    faceLeft: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Action_Slave_Default'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(6)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(4500)
      setAngleY: -35000
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(8000)
      setAngleY: -35000
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(3)
    setAngleY: -70000
  endIf: 
  storeValue: Mem(StunTime), Val(10000)
  storeValue: Mem(TumbleTime), Val(1)
  runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    sendSignalToAction: s32'cmnWorldSideBreakObj', (SIGNAL0)
  endRunOnObject: 
  addMoveForceDisableFlag: -2147483648
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(2)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Up'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(3)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Down'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(4)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Bound'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(5)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Event'
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(6)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(1500)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_6'
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(4500)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_6_4500'
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(8000)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_6_8000'
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(3)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(4500)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_3_4500'
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(21000)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_3_21000'
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(ActReg0)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_6'
    debugLogForScript: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_Error', 0, 0
  endIf: 
  else: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
  endElse: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_6'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'dash'
  moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
  addPositionX: 0, -1500000
  setPositionY: 0
  landingHeight: 0
  physicsXImpulse: 0, 100000
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Slide'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      landingHeight: 0
      addPositionX: 0, -500000
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(16)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', 166
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          haltMomentum: 1
          setPositionXInBattle: 150000
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Slide_6', (PLAYER)
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(30)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(10), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(1092000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(2184000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(20)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Slide', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Slide_6'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 1
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
    linkCommonPawn: 
    linkObjPosition: 3
    flipDirection: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Finish'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  moveCameraBasePosObject: (SELF)
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_Slide_6', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_Slide_6', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 60, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, -15000, 0, 15000, 0, 80, 0, 70, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetX: 0, -50000, 0, -50000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetZ: 0, 135000, 0, 135000, 0, 30, 0, 50, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraStart: 
  sprite: s32'null', 20
  moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, -15000, 0, 15000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetX: 0, 0, 0, -100000, 0, 40, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  sprite: s32'null', 20
  centerScreenPosition: 0, 450, 0, 0
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_Slide_6', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 25, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraFOV: 0, 95, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraBasePosOffsetY: 0, 250000, 0, 250000, 0, 0, 0, 25, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  endLabel: 
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Up_6'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Up'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'jump'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      landingHeight: 0
      addPositionX: 0, -1250000
      setPositionY: 1750000
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(16)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (FALL_SPEED)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
        upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          upon: (IDLING)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(5)
              clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
              haltMomentum: 1
              setPositionXInBattle: 150000
            endIf: 
          endUpon: 
        endUpon: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Up_6'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Up_6', (PLAYER)
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(60)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(15), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(10920000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(21840000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(50)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Up', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  setDepthSpeed: 0, 12500
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Val(-12500)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setDepth: 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Down_6'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Down'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'jump'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      landingHeight: 0
      addPositionX: 0, -1250000
      setPositionY: 1750000
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(16)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (FALL_SPEED)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
        upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          upon: (IDLING)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(5)
              clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
              haltMomentum: 1
              setPositionXInBattle: 150000
            endIf: 
          endUpon: 
        endUpon: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
endSubroutine:

  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_Bound_6', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 100, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, -15000, 0, 15000, 0, 80, 0, 70, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetX: 0, -50000, 0, -50000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetZ: 0, 135000, 0, -75000, 0, 30, 0, 50, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTrackUp: 0, 0, 0, 100000, 0, 50, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraStart: 
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetZ: 0, 0, 0, 150000, 0, 30, 0, 50, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  sprite: s32'null', 20
  moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, -15000, 0, 15000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetX: 0, 0, 0, -100000, 0, 40, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetZ: 0, 0, 0, 75000, 0, 30, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  sprite: s32'null', 20
  centerScreenPosition: 0, 450, 0, 0
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_Bound_6', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 25, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
