beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_6_4500'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Slide'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'dash'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      addPositionX: 0, -1000000
      setPositionY: 0
      landingHeight: 0
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(20)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', 166
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          haltMomentum: 1
          setPositionXInBattle: 150000
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6_4500'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Slide_6_L', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(10), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(43680000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Slide', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  setDepthSpeed: 0, 46666
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Val(-46666)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setDepth: 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Slide_6_L'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 1
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
    linkCommonPawn: 
    linkObjPosition: 3
    flipDirection: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Finish'

  sprite: s32'null', 1

  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraFOV: 0, 95, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'

  moveCameraBasePosOffsetY: 0, 250000, 0, 250000, 0, 0, 0, 25, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  centerScreenPosition: 0, 231, 0, 0

              clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)

      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)

      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0

      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Down', 0

              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)

            endElse:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Bound_6_4500'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Bound'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'jump'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      landingHeight: 0
      addPositionX: 0, -1250000
      setPositionY: 1750000
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(16)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (FALL_SPEED)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
        upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          upon: (IDLING)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(5)
              clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
              haltMomentum: 1
              setPositionXInBattle: 150000
            endIf: 
          endUpon: 
        endUpon: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Bound_6_4500'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'gorogoro'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Bound_6_L', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(10), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(43680000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Bound', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)

    endUpon:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_6_8000'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Slide'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'dash'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      addPositionX: 0, -1000000
      setPositionY: 0
      landingHeight: 0
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(20)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', 166
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          haltMomentum: 1
          setPositionXInBattle: 150000
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6_8000'
  checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'WSB_Slave_Bound'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'gorogoro'
  endIf: 
  else: 
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  endElse: 
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Slide_6_8000', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(10), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(43680000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Max'
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
      ifNot: Mem(ReturnValue)
        cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      endIf: 
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Slide', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
      sendSignalToAction: s32'cmn_wsb_landing_finish', (SIGNAL9)
      sendSignalToAction: s32'cmn_wsb_landing', (SIGNAL9)
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  setDepthSpeed: 0, 88888
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Val(-88888)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setDepth: 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

  moveCameraBasePosOffsetY: 0, 250000, 0, 250000, 0, 0, 0, 25, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  centerScreenPosition: 0, 231, 0, 0
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Up_6_8000'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Up'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'jump'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      landingHeight: 0
      addPositionX: 0, -1250000
      setPositionY: 1750000
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(16)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (FALL_SPEED)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
        upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          upon: (IDLING)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(5)
              clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
              haltMomentum: 1
              setPositionXInBattle: 150000
            endIf: 
          endUpon: 
        endUpon: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Up_6_8000'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Up_6_8000', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(15), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(43680000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(87360000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Up', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  setDepthSpeed: 0, 88888
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Val(-88888)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setDepth: 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Up_6_8000'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 1
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
    linkCommonPawn: 
    linkObjPosition: 3
    flipDirection: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Finish'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  moveCameraBasePosObject: (SELF)
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_Up_6_8000', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_Up_6_8000', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 130, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, -15000, 0, 15000, 0, 80, 0, 70, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetX: 0, -50000, 0, -50000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetZ: 0, 135000, 0, -75000, 0, 30, 0, 50, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTrackUp: 0, 0, 0, 100000, 0, 50, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraStart: 
  sprite: s32'null', 50
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetZ: 0, 0, 0, 150000, 0, 30, 0, 50, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  sprite: s32'null', 20
  moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, -15000, 0, 15000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetX: 0, 0, 0, -100000, 0, 40, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffsetZ: 0, 0, 0, 75000, 0, 30, 0, 100, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_WorldSideBreak_Up_6_8000', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 25, s32'linear'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 1000, 0, 1000, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraFOV: 0, 95, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 25, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraTrackUp: 0, 100000, 0, 0, 0, 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'accel_brake_test'
  moveCameraBasePosOffsetY: 0, 250000, 0, 250000, 0, 0, 0, 25, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
  centerScreenPosition: 0, 231, 0, 0
endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Slide_3_4500'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Slide'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'dash'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      addPositionX: 0, -1000000
      setPositionY: 0
      landingHeight: 0
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(20)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', 166
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          haltMomentum: 1
          setPositionXInBattle: 150000
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_3_4500'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Slide_3', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(10), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(43680000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(87360000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Slide', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  setDepthSpeed: 0, 176666
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Val(-176666)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setDepth: 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Down', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  setDepthSpeed: 0, 176666
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Val(-176666)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setDepth: 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon:

      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)

      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1

      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (FALL_SPEED)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)

          gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'

              clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)

              setPositionXInBattle: 150000

          endUpon:

      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Bound_3_4500'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'gorogoro'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Bound_3', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(10), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(43680000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(87360000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Bound', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)

            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)

            endElse:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_3_21000_ST'
  checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'WSB_Slave_Bound'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'gorogoro'
  endIf: 
  else: 
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  endElse: 
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(0)
    createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Slide_3', (PLAYER)
  endIf: 
  else: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(1)
      createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Down_3_L', (PLAYER)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Up_3_L', (PLAYER)
    endElse: 
  endElse: 
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(15), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(65520000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(131040000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(1500000)
  ifNot: Mem(BattleDoing)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(2)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(43680000)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(87360000)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(50000000)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(0)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(65520000)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(87360000)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(50000000)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(28392000)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(56784000)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(50000000)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(2)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(65520000)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(0)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(64428000)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(1)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(131040000)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(87360000)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(1350000)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endElse: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    pushVelocityY: 
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
    warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
    popVelocityY: 
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      if: Mem(BattleDoing)
        cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
        cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      endIf: 
      else: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(1)
          cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
          cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Slide', 0
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(1)
                if: Mem(Dir)
                  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(PosXRaw), Val(690000)
                    warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-746000), Val(0), Val(5)
                  endIf: 
                  else: 
                    warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
                  endElse: 
                endIf: 
                else: 
                  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosXRaw), Val(-690000)
                    warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-734000), Val(0), Val(5)
                  endIf: 
                  else: 
                    warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
                  endElse: 
                endElse: 
              endIf: 
              else: 
                warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              endElse: 
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  setDepthSpeed: 0, 777222
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Val(-777222)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setDepth: 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Up_3_21000'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Up'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'jump'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      landingHeight: 0
      addPositionX: 0, -1250000
      setPositionY: 1750000
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(16)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (FALL_SPEED)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
        upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          upon: (IDLING)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(5)
              clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
              haltMomentum: 1
              setPositionXInBattle: 150000
            endIf: 
          endUpon: 
        endUpon: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Up_3_21000'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Up_3_L', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(15), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(65520000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(131040000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(1500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    pushVelocityY: 
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
    warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
    popVelocityY: 
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Up', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)

      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon:

      setDepth: 0

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Master_Bound_3_21000'
  upon: (FRAME_STEP)
    moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    displayModel: 0
    setNoCollision: 0
  endUpon: 
  upon: (SIGNAL_NAME)
    checkSignalName: s32'WSB_Bound'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL_NAME)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
      displayModel: 1
      setNoCollision: 1
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'jump'
      moveToObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      landingHeight: 0
      addPositionX: 0, -1250000
      setPositionY: 1750000
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(100000), Val(0), Val(16)
      setDepth: 0
      setAngleY: 0
      upon: (FALL_SPEED)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
        upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
          warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(150000), Val(0), Val(5)
          upon: (IDLING)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(5)
              clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
              haltMomentum: 1
              setPositionXInBattle: 150000
            endIf: 
          endUpon: 
        endUpon: 
      endUpon: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Bound_3_21000'
  gotoLabelRequests: s32'gorogoro'
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Bound_3_L', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(90)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(10), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(43680000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(87360000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(1500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(SpeedY), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg5)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
  upon: (FALL_SPEED)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (FALL_SPEED)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
    pushVelocityY: 
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
    warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg6)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1)
    popVelocityY: 
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(80)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg6), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
        modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(Gravity), Val(2)
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
      haltMomentum: 1
      warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-700000), Val(0), Val(15)
      setAngleY: 0
      effectForDownLv2: 129, 1, 0
      effectForDownLv3: 129, 1, 0
      cameraShake: s32'ShakeTateYoko', 500, 0, 10, 5
      sendSignalName: 32, s32'WSB_Bound', 0
      cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Down_Def_Stone_M'
      voiceLine: s16'vxxx109'
      upon: (IDLING)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(10)
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashstart', (BACK_1_BODY)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(15)
          if: Mem(HitPoint)
            if: Mem(CmnCharaReg7)
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-750000), Val(0), Val(5)
              gotoLabelRequests: s32'brake'
            endIf: 
            else: 
              warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Val(-775000), Val(0), Val(5)
              jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            jumpToStateKeepDamage: s32'CmnActKorogari'
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(20)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          setPositionXInBattle: -750000
          haltMomentum: 1
          createArgDirection: 1
          createParticleWithArg: s32'bg_dashbrake', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  setDepthSpeed: 0, 777222
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(PosZ), Val(-777222)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      setDepth: 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_wallbreak_eff'
  ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
  ignoreFinishStop: 1
  deactivateObjectByNameAll: s32'cmn_wallbreak_lv1'
  deactivateObjectByNameAll: s32'cmn_wallbreak_lv2'
  deactivateObjectByNameAll: s32'cmn_wallbreak_lv3'
  setObjectSize: 1250
  checkMoveFlag: (CLOSE_TO_RIGHT_CORNER)
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    faceLeft: 
  endIf: 
  checkMoveFlag: (CLOSE_TO_LEFT_CORNER)
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    faceRight: 
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(SentToObject0)
    addPositionX: 0, -150000
    addPositionY: 0, 75000
    addDepth: 0, -150000
    setAngleY: -15000
  endIf: 
  else: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(6)
      addPositionX: 0, 150000
      addPositionY: 0, 75000
      addDepth: 0, -50000
      setAngleY: -30000
    endIf: 
    else: 
      addPositionX: 0, 125000
      addPositionY: 0, 75000
      addDepth: 0, 75000
      setAngleY: 30000
    endElse: 
  endElse: 
  if: Mem(SentToObject1)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(6)
      setAngleY: -10000
    endIf: 
    else: 
      setAngleY: 50000
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(BattleDoing)
    checkStageName: s16'WhiteHouse_PL'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(0)
        ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(3)
          setAngleY: 210000
          addDepth: 0, 100000
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    checkStageName: s16'Station_PL'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(0)
        ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(3)
          setAngleY: 90000
          addPositionX: 0, -180000
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

      cameraShakeEX: s32'shake_temae', 500, 0, 10, 0, s32'Curve_Linear'
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
      cameraShakeEX: s32'shake_temae', 5000, 0, 10, 0, s32'Curve_Linear'
    endIf:

    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(SpeedY), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY)

      velocityXPercent: 96
      velocityYPercent: 99

    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Effect_NoStop_or_Delete'
  ifNot: Mem(FuncArg0)
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      if: Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        stopLinkObject: 0
        ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
        ignoreFinishStop: 1
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
  else: 
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      if: Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
        deactivateCurrentObject: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endElse: 
endSubroutine:

        endIf:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnDS_Initialize'
  upon: (IDLING)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(1)
      ifNot: Mem(ActReg0)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        setLightRedColor: 100
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(1)
          enableSuperArmor: 1
          superArmorType: (ARMOR)
          superArmorHitstop: 30, 30
          setThrowInvulnerable: 1
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(120)
          jumpToState: s32'_NEUTRAL'
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(2)
      ifNot: Mem(ActReg0)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        setLightBlueColor: 100
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(1)
          attackCollisionForceExpand: 1
          ignoreInvuln: 1
          hitStop: 60
          attackEnemySpriteFix: 1
          grabOrRelease: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(2)
          initializeAttackCategoryByCurrent: 
          attackCollisionForceExpand: 1
          grabOrRelease: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(120)
          jumpToState: s32'_NEUTRAL'
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(10)
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(47)
        ifNot: Mem(ActReg0)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
          setLightGreenColor: 100
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(1)
            initializeAttackCategoryByCurrent: 
            attackLevel: 2
            damage: 0, 30
            attackCollisionForceExpand: 1
            displayHitSparks: 1
            disableHitstopForSelf: 1
            grabOrRelease: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(10)
              atkAngle: 0
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(11)
              atkAngle: -90
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(12)
              atkAngle: 90
              angleGuardForce: 90
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(13)
              atkAngle: -90
              angleGuardForce: -90
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(14)
              attackLevel: 0
              damage: 0, 10
              groundHitEffect: (FORCE_STAND)
              airHitEffect: (FORCE_STAND)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(15)
              attackLevel: 1
              damage: 0, 20
              groundHitEffect: (FORCE_STAND)
              airHitEffect: (FORCE_STAND)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(16)
              attackLevel: 2
              damage: 0, 30
              groundHitEffect: (FORCE_STAND)
              airHitEffect: (FORCE_STAND)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(DebugSkillEx), Val(17)
              attackLevel: 3
              damage: 0, 40
              groundHitEffect: (FORCE_STAND)
              airHitEffect: (FORCE_STAND)
            endIf:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Collision_test'
  createObjectWithArg: s32'cmn_Collision_test', (PLAYER)
  storeValueFromObject: (PREVIOUS), Mem(ActReg0), (SELF), Mem(FuncArg0)
  storeValueFromObject: (PREVIOUS), Mem(ActReg1), (SELF), Mem(FuncArg1)
  storeValueFromObject: (PREVIOUS), Mem(ActReg2), (SELF), Mem(FuncArg2)
  storeValueFromObject: (PREVIOUS), Mem(ActReg3), (SELF), Mem(FuncArg3)
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmn_Collision_test'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    setLinkObjectDestroyOnStateChange: 3
    stopLinkObject: 3
    linkObjPosition: 3
    collisionDisplay: 1
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(SentToObject0)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
        deactivateCurrentObject: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (PRE_HIT_COLLISION)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (PRE_HIT_COLLISION)
      ifNot: Mem(SentToObject1)
        appendCollisionEx: 1, 2, 45, 2, 46, 2, 47, 2, 48
        runOnObject: (PLAYER)
          linkObjectCollision: 1
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        appendCollisionEx: 0, 2, 45, 2, 46, 2, 47, 2, 48
        invulnForce: 0
        damageTransferToPlayer: 1, s32'cmn_Collision_test_Param'
      endElse: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 60
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_Collision_test_Param'
  tensionGainOnConnect: 0
  damagePercent: 0
  riscConsume: 0
  disableExtraRiscConsume: 1
  dontAddComboCount: 1
endSubroutine:

    setPositionYByScreenPercentage: 20
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(PosY)
      storeValue: Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg0)
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnZokuseiDmgCheckFunc'
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
  ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(FuncArg0)
    ifOperationInObject: (IS_GREATER), (PLAYER), Mem(DamageEffectCount), Val(0)
      ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(PlayerDamage)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(ActReg0)
    deactivateCurrentObject: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnDmgFire'

  ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
    createObject: s32'cmn_dmg_fire', (CENTER)
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginState: s32'cmn_Dust_alarm'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    setLinkObjectDestroyOnStateChange: 3
    setLinkObjectDestroyOnDamage: 3
    linkObjPosition: 3
    ignoreSlowdown: 1
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Effect_Angle'
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_Effect_NoLink'
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      if: Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(20)
          stopLinkObject: 0
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
          ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Settings'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 3
  sprite: s32'null', 7
  linkParticle: s32'cmn_dust_alarm'
  cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_SYS_DustStart'
  sprite: s32'null', 25
  linkObjPosition: 0
endState:

    setLinkObjectDestroyOnStateChange: 3
    setLinkObjectDestroyOnDamage: 3

          stopLinkObject: 0
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
          ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Settings'
  endUpon:

  linkObjPosition: 0

  ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
    calcDistanceEx: 2, 3, 100, 25, 100

      attackHitPositionType: 3, 1, 0
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginState: s32'cmn_KizetsuLoop'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
    upon: (SIGNAL0)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL0)
        storeValue: Mem(PgActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'dead'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL1)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL1)
        storeValue: Mem(PgActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'dead'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL2)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL2)
        storeValue: Mem(PgActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'dead'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL3)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL3)
        storeValue: Mem(PgActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'dead'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL4)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(4)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL4)
        storeValue: Mem(PgActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'dead'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL5)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(5)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL5)
        storeValue: Mem(PgActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'dead'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL6)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(6)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL6)
        storeValue: Mem(PgActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'dead'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (SIGNAL7)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(7)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL7)
        storeValue: Mem(PgActReg0), Val(1)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'dead'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      callPrivateFunction: s32'KizetsuKaiten', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0
    endUpon: 
    linkParticle: s32'cmn_kizetu'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
  endLabel: 
  beginLabel: s32'dead'
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  physicsYImpulse: 0, 5000
  setAlphaColorSpeed: -10
endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Check'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(1)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near01'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(2)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near02'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(3)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near03'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(4)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Far03'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(5)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Far04'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(6)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Projectile'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(7)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Up'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(8)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Down'
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(AdjustmentForScript0), Val(9)
    finishCameraRequest: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Zoom'
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginState: s32'cmn_kakusei_finish'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ignoreFinishStop: 1
      ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
      fadeOutStart: 0, 0
      linkObjectDirection: 2
      linkObjectSize: 2
      linkObjPosition: 2
      upon: (PRE_DRAW)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PRE_DRAW)
        createArgTransPriority: -100
        linkParticleWithArg2: s32'cmn_kakusei_finish_total'
        storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Angle), (PARENT), Mem(Angle)
        storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(AngleY), (PARENT), Mem(AngleY)
        storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(AngleX), (PARENT), Mem(AngleX)
      endUpon: 
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 120
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  endLabel: 
  fadeInStart: 30
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Screen_Effect'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    hideUI: 1
    cinesco: 1
    ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 1
    ignoreFinishStop: 1
    ignoreZLine: 1
    cameraShake: s32'ShakeTate', 1500, 5, 25, 0
    runOnObject: (WINNER)
      slowMoveRate: 0, 3000
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (LOSER)
      slowMoveRate: 0, 3000
    endRunOnObject: 
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg1), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY)
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg2), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(2), Mem(ActReg3)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        slowMoveRate: 0, 1000
      endRunOnObject: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          slowMoveRate: 0, 2000
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY), Val(50000)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          slowMoveRate: 0, 500
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterSlowSettings'
    resetSaturation: 1, 1
    setPostProcessSaturation: -1, 800, 40
    resetDiffusion: 1, 1
    setDiffusionLuminance: -1, 1400, 50
    setDiffusionThreshold: -1, 0, 50
    resetDOF: 1, 1
    focalDistance: -1, 700, 0
    focalRegion: -1, 0, 0
    focalNearTransition: -1, 0, 0
    focalFarTransition: -1, 500, 0
    focalNearBlurSize: -1, 0, 0
    focalFarBlurSize: -1, 5, 10
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
    createGlareEffect: 1
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Mem(Tmp)
    setGlareColor: 2, 45, 0, 127, 0, 255, 0, 255, 0, 255
    setGlareScale: 2, 45, 0, 1200, 0, 1200
    ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(Dir)
      setGlareOffset: 2, 45, 0, -300000, 0, -300000
    endIf: 
    else: 
      setGlareOffset: 2, 45, 0, 300000, 0, -300000
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 120
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  resetDOF: 0, 30
  resetSaturation: 0, 30
  resetDiffusion: 0, 30
  removeGlareEffect: 2, 45
  cinesco: 0
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  hideUI: 0
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Screen_NoProce'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    hideUI: 1
    cinesco: 1
    ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 1
    ignoreFinishStop: 1
    ignoreZLine: 1
    cameraShake: s32'ShakeTate', 1500, 5, 25, 0
    runOnObject: (WINNER)
      slowMoveRate: 0, 3000
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (LOSER)
      slowMoveRate: 0, 3000
    endRunOnObject: 
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg1), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY)
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg2), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(2), Mem(ActReg3)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        slowMoveRate: 0, 1000
      endRunOnObject: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          slowMoveRate: 0, 2000
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY), Val(50000)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          slowMoveRate: 0, 500
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterSlowSettings'
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
    createGlareEffect: 1
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Mem(Tmp)
    setGlareColor: 2, 45, 0, 127, 0, 255, 0, 255, 0, 255
    setGlareScale: 2, 45, 0, 1200, 0, 1200
    ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(Dir)
      setGlareOffset: 2, 45, 0, -300000, 0, -300000
    endIf: 
    else: 
      setGlareOffset: 2, 45, 0, 300000, 0, -300000
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 120
  sprite: s32'null', 30
  removeGlareEffect: 2, 45
  cinesco: 0
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  hideUI: 0
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Pattern'
  ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
    if: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
      createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Screen_Effect', (PLAYER)
      cameraShakeEX: s32'Depth', 500, 0, 150, 0, s32'shake_easeout'
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyDistanceX), Val(600000)
        stackObjectEx: (SELF), 4, 14, 24
        isObjectActive: (STACK0)
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          ifTrueInObject: (STACK0), Mem(IsPlayer)
            setRandom: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1), Val(3)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
              createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near01', (PLAYER)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
              createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Far03', (PLAYER)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
              createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Far04', (PLAYER)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Projectile', (PLAYER)
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        else: 
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Projectile', (PLAYER)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyDiffY), Val(120000)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Up', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyDiffY), Val(-40000)
            createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Down', (PLAYER)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(EnemyDistanceX), Val(300000)
              setRandom: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1), Val(3)
              if: Mem(IsTo3)
                setRandom: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1), Val(2)
              endIf: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Zoom', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near02', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near03', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
            endIf: 
            else: 
              setRandom: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1), Val(3)
              if: Mem(IsTo3)
                setRandom: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1), Val(2)
              endIf: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near01', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near02', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near03', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
            endElse: 
          endElse: 
        endElse: 
      endElse: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
  createObject: s32'cmnCam_FinishTimeOut', (PLAYER)
  deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Pattern_ex'
  ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
    if: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
      createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Screen_Effect', (PLAYER)
      cameraShakeEX: s32'Depth', 500, 0, 150, 0, s32'shake_easeout'
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyDistanceX), Val(600000)
        stackObjectEx: (SELF), 4, 14, 24
        isObjectActive: (STACK0)
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          ifTrueInObject: (STACK0), Mem(IsPlayer)
            setRandom: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1), Val(3)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
              createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near01', (PLAYER)

            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)

            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
              createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Far04', (PLAYER)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Projectile', (PLAYER)
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        else: 
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Projectile', (PLAYER)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyDiffY), Val(120000)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Up', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(EnemyDiffY), Val(-40000)
            createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Down', (PLAYER)
          endIf: 
          else: 
            ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(EnemyDistanceX), Val(300000)
              setRandom: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1), Val(2)
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Zoom', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near02', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
            endIf: 
            else: 
              setRandom: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1), Val(2)
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near01', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
              ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
                createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near02', (PLAYER)
              endIf: 
            endElse: 
          endElse: 
        endElse: 
      endElse: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
  createObject: s32'cmnCam_FinishTimeOut', (PLAYER)
  deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_FinishCamera'
  ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
    if: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
      createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Screen_Effect', (PLAYER)
      cameraShakeEX: s32'Depth', 500, 0, 150, 0, s32'shake_easeout'
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near01', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near02', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near03', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(4)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Far03', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(5)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Far04', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(6)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Projectile', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(7)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Up', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(8)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Down', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(9)
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Zoom', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
  createObject: s32'cmnCam_FinishTimeOut', (PLAYER)
  deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Pattern_1'

endState:

beginState: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Up'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Init'
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnInitializeThrowBaseAndTarget', Val(-1000000), Val(1000000), Val(-1300000), Val(1200000)
    moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 4, 21, s32'brake'
    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, -30000, 0, 440000, 0, 5000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 30000, 0, 200000, 0, 65000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'accel_brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 800, 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 800, 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, 0, 0, -12500, 0, 30, 0, 200, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'linear'
    moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_Finish_Air01', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 200, s32'linear'
    moveCameraFOV: 0, 80, 0, 30, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
    setPosXBetweenObject: 13, 13
    setPosYBetweenObject: 13, 13
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(PosY), Val(0)
      setPositionY: 0
    endIf: 
    runOnObject: (STACK0)
      setPosXBetweenObject: 13, 14
      setPosYBetweenObject: 13, 14
    endRunOnObject: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 120
  setMotionBlurAmount: 100
  cameraShakeEX: s32'Impact', 500, 0, 40, 0, s32'shake_easeout'
  sprite: s32'null', 10
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 135000, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'accel_brake'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 200, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_Finish_Air01', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 30, s32'brake'
  moveCameraFOV: 0, 65, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  focalDistance: 700, 0, 0
  focalRegion: 0, 0, 0
  focalNearTransition: 0, 0, 0
  focalFarTransition: 500, 0, 0
  focalNearBlurSize: 0, 0, 0
  focalFarBlurSize: 40, 0, 0
  resetDOF: 0, 30
  resetSaturation: 0, 30
  resetDiffusion: 0, 30
  sprite: s32'null', 10
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
  cinesco: 0
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  hideUI: 0
endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Down'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCrossup'
    if: Mem(ReturnValue)
      flipDirection: 
    endIf: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Init'
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnInitializeThrowBaseAndTarget', Val(-1000000), Val(1000000), Val(-1300000), Val(1200000)
    moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 4, 21, s32'brake'
    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, -30000, 0, 440000, 0, 600000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 40000, 0, 50000, 0, 65000, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'accel_brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 800, 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 800, 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRoll: 0, 0, 0, 18500, 0, 30, 0, 200, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
