    moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_Finish_Air01', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 200, s32'linear'
    moveCameraFOV: 0, 80, 0, 30, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
    setPosXBetweenObject: 13, 13
    setPosYBetweenObject: 13, 13
    addPositionY: 0, 48000
    runOnObject: (STACK0)
      setPosXBetweenObject: 13, 14
      setPosYBetweenObject: 14, 14
    endRunOnObject: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 120
  setMotionBlurAmount: 100
  cameraShakeEX: s32'Impact', 500, 0, 40, 0, s32'shake_easeout'
  sprite: s32'null', 10
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 135000, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'accel_brake'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 400, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'

  moveCameraFOV: 0, 65, 0, 35, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
  focalDistance: 700, 0, 0
  focalRegion: 0, 0, 0
  focalNearTransition: 0, 0, 0
  focalFarTransition: 500, 0, 0
  focalNearBlurSize: 0, 0, 0
  focalFarBlurSize: 40, 0, 0
  resetDOF: 0, 30

  sprite: s32'null', 20

endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnCrossup'
  returnValue: 0, 0
  ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER), (WINNER), Mem(EnemyFrontDistance), Val(0)
    returnValue: 0, 1
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Zoom'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Init'
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnInitializeThrowBaseAndTarget', Val(-1000000), Val(1000000), Val(-1300000), Val(1200000)
    moveCameraTargetCameraOnBlend: 4, 12, s32'brake'
    moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, 40000, 0, 440000, 0, 105000, 0, 0, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 40000, 0, 50000, 0, 105000, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'accel_brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 800, 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetRotRateYaw: 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 800, 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
    moveCameraTargetPercent: 0, 100, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 200, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'

    moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_Finish_Zoom', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 200, s32'linear'
    moveCameraFOV: 0, 68, 0, 30, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
    upon: (FRAME_STEP)
      setPosXBetweenObject: 13, 13
      setPosYBetweenObject: 13, 13
      runOnObject: (STACK0)
        setPosXBetweenObject: 13, 14
        setPosYBetweenObject: 13, 13
      endRunOnObject: 
    endUpon: 
    ifOperationInObject: (IS_GREATER), (WINNER), Mem(Physique), Val(1)
      moveCameraTrackUp: 0, 0, 0, -30000, 0, 15, 0, 105, 0, 30, s32'brake', s32'brake'
      moveCameraFOV: 0, 70, 0, 30, 0, 150, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 10
  setMotionBlurAmount: 100

  moveCameraBasePosOffset: 0, 40000, 0, 440000, 0, 105000, 0, 108, 0, 42, 0, 0, s32'linear', s32'brake'
  sprite: s32'null', 10
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
  moveCameraTargetPosOffset: 0, 60000, 0, 0, 0, 135000, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'accel_brake'
  moveCameraTargetPosRate: 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraTargetRotRate: 0, 800, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraSplinePosRate: 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'brake', s32'brake'
  moveCameraSpline: s32'cmn_Finish_Zoom', 0, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 30, s32'brake'
  moveCameraFOV: 0, 65, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, s32'accel_brake', s32'brake'
  resetDOF: 0, 30
  resetSaturation: 0, 30
  resetDiffusion: 0, 30
  sprite: s32'null', 20
  moveCameraOrthoCurve: s32'orthoone', 0, 0, s32'orthoone'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
  cinesco: 0

endState: 

beginState: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Tilt'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Init'

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Init'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
    fadeOutStart: 300, 1
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      fadeInStart: 0
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      fadeInStart: 0
    endRunOnObject: 
    ifNot: Mem(IsTo3)
      runOnObject: (PLAYER)
        ignoreZLine: 1
      endRunOnObject: 
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        ignoreZLine: 1
      endRunOnObject: 
    endIf: 
    runOnObject: (WINNER)
      slowMoveRate: 0, 3000
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (LOSER)
      slowMoveRate: 0, 3000
    endRunOnObject: 
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg1), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY)
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg2), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(2), Mem(ActReg3)
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
      runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
        slowMoveRate: 0, 1000
      endRunOnObject: 
      ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          slowMoveRate: 0, 2000
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosY), Val(50000)
        runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
          slowMoveRate: 0, 500
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnCamCounterSlowSettings'
    resetSaturation: 1, 1
    setPostProcessSaturation: -1, 800, 40
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnGlareDelete'
    createGlareEffect: 1
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Mem(Tmp)
    setGlareColor: 2, 45, 0, 127, 0, 255, 0, 255, 0, 255
    setGlareScale: 2, 45, 0, 1200, 0, 1200
    ifTrueInObject: (WINNER), Mem(Dir)
      setGlareOffset: 2, 45, 0, -300000, 0, -300000
    endIf: 
    else: 
      setGlareOffset: 2, 45, 0, 300000, 0, -300000
    endElse: 
    upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
      resetSaturation: 0, 20
      resetDOF: 0, 40
      removeGlareEffect: 2, 45
    endUpon: 
    cinesco: 1
    hideUI: 1
    ignoreFinishStop: 1
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
    ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
      deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
        linkObjectDirection: 2
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near01', (PLAYER)
          addPositionY: 0, 600000
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near02', (PLAYER)
          addPositionY: 0, 400000
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Near03', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(4)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Far04', (PLAYER)
          addPositionY: 0, 300000
          setAngleY: -75000
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(5)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Zoom', (PLAYER)
          addPositionY: 0, 300000
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(6)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Tilt', (PLAYER)
          addPositionY: 0, 400000
          setAngleY: 40000
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(7)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Projectile', (PLAYER)
          addPositionY: 0, 0
          setAngleY: 70000
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(8)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Up', (PLAYER)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(9)
          createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Down', (PLAYER)
          setAngleX: -30000
          setAngleY: 60000
        endIf: 
        createObjectWithArg: s32'cmn_kakusei_finish', (PLAYER)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        createObject: s32'cmn_FinishCamera_Screen_Effect', (PLAYER)
        cameraShakeEX: s32'Depth', 2000, 0, 150, 0, s32'shake_easeout'
      endElse: 
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginState: s32'cmn_hijump_obj'
  sprite: s32'null', 40
  linkParticle: s32'cmn_hijump'
  setObjectHeight: 3000
  linkObjPosition: 2
  stopLinkObject: 2
  setLinkObjectDestroyOnDamage: 2
  setAlphaColor: 0
  upon: (IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(2)
      checkCurrentStateName: (PARENT), s32'CmnActJump'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        setAlphaColor: 255
        ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(8)
          storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(SpeedX), (PARENT), Mem(SpeedX)
          storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(SpeedY), (PARENT), Mem(SpeedY)
          setAngleBySpeed: 90000
          haltMomentum: 1
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endState:

beginState: s32'cmn_AfroObj'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    linkObjectAngle: 3
    linkObjectZ: 3
    linkObjectDirection: 3
    linkObjectColor: 3
    linkObjectMaterialSet: 3
    linkObjectCommonMaterialParam: 3
    ignoreHideAllButSelf: 1
    ignoreSuperFreeze: 1
    ignoreFinishStop: 1
    ignoreSlowdown: 1
    ignoreHiddenByDisplayOnlySelf: 32, 1
    if: Mem(SentToObject0)
      createObjectWithArg: s32'cmn_Afro_Timer', (CENTER)
      if: Mem(IsFriendsCutScene)
        ignoreHiddenByDisplayOnlySelf: 3, 1
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      createObjectWithArg: s32'cmn_Afro_Timer_CS', (CENTER)
      if: Mem(IsFriendsCutScene)
        ignoreHiddenByDisplayOnlySelf: 3, 1
      endIf: 
      if: Mem(IsEnemysCutScene)
        ignoreHiddenByDisplayOnlySelf: 32, 1
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
    upon: (PRE_DRAW)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (PRE_DRAW)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmn_AfroCheck'
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
  upon: (IDLING)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_AfroCheck'
  endUpon: 
  upon: (AFTER_EXIT)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg0), Val(1)
      callPrivateFunction: s32'ans_ScarfOn', 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_AfroCheck'
  ifNot: Mem(Afro)
    callSubroutine: s32'Afro_Delete'
    ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
      createArgFromSocket: s32'Afro', 0, 3
      createParticleWithArg2: s32'cmn_afro_end', (PLAYER)
    endIf: 
    deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg1), Val(1)
    checkDisplayedMesh: (PLAYER), s32'Edy_Head'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      checkDisplayedMesh: (PLAYER), s32'Edy_head_pattern'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        checkDisplayedMesh: (PLAYER), s32'Edyx_skeleton'
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
        endElse: 
      endElse: 
    endElse: 
    ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg1)
      detatchPawnFromSocket: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_Low', s32'Afro'
        changeDefaultMeshSet: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        attachPawn: s32'Edy_Head', s32'Afro'
        swapMeshSet: s32'edy'
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
        attachPawn: s32'Edy_head_pattern', s32'Afro'
        swapMeshSet: s32'edy'
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
        attachPawn: s32'Edyx_skeleton', s32'Afro'
        swapMeshSet: s32'edy'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg1), Val(2)
    checkDisplayedMesh: (PLAYER), s32'Head_Low_DI'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
    endElse: 
    ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg1)
      detatchPawnFromSocket: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_Low', s32'Afro'
        changeDefaultMeshSet: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_Low_DI', s32'Afro'
        swapMeshSet: s32'DI'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg1), Val(3)
    checkDisplayedMesh: (PLAYER), s32'Head_High_DI'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
    endElse: 
    ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg1)
      detatchPawnFromSocket: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_High', s32'Afro'
        changeDefaultMeshSet: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_High_DI', s32'Afro'
        swapMeshSet: s32'DI'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg1), Val(4)
    checkDisplayedMesh: (PLAYER), s32'Head_DI'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
    endElse: 
    ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg1)
      detatchPawnFromSocket: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_Low', s32'Afro'
        changeDefaultMeshSet: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_DI', s32'Afro'
        swapMeshSet: s32'DI'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg1), Val(5)
    checkDisplayedMesh: (PLAYER), s32'Head_shadow'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
    endElse: 
    ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActReg1)
      detatchPawnFromSocket: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_Low', s32'Afro'
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
        attachPawn: s32'Head_shadow', s32'Afro'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  endIf: 
  callSubroutine: s32'Afro_Check'
  ifNot: Mem(IsWorldStopperOther)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ObjReg0), Val(1)
      callPrivateFunction: s32'ans_ScarfUpdate', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginState: s32'cmn_Afro_Timer'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    stopLinkObject: 3
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(10)
    upon: (PLAYER_GUARD_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
      ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(DmgFire)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_GUARD_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'Bomb'
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(0)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(120)
        if: Mem(IsTo3)
          stackObjectEx: (SELF), 4, 3, 24
          stackObjectEx: (SELF), 4, 4, 3
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_GUARD_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
      ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(DmgFire)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_GUARD_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'Bomb'
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(0)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(15)
        if: Mem(IsTo3)
          stackObjectEx: (SELF), 4, 3, 24
          stackObjectEx: (SELF), 4, 4, 3
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_GUARD_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
          gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
    endUpon: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(600)
    upon: (IDLING)
      ifNot: Mem(IsSomebodysCutSceneOrSelfHide)
        ifNot: Mem(CheckStop)
          ifNot: Mem(IsRoundTimerStop)
            if: Mem(BattleDoing)
              ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg18)
                modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg5), Val(1)
                checkMoveFlag: (DEBUG)
                if: Mem(Tmp)
                  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(540)
                    ifOperation: (MOD_EQUALS_0), Mem(ActReg5), Val(5)
                      debugLogForScript: s32'Timer', 2, 50
                    endIf: 
                  endIf: 
                  else: 
                    ifOperation: (MOD_EQUALS_0), Mem(ActReg5), Val(60)
                      debugLogForScript: s32'Timer', 2, 50
                    endIf: 
                  endElse: 
                endIf: 
                ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg2)
                  clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_GUARD_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
                  clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
                  clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
                  gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
                endIf: 
              endIf: 
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      ifNotInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(Afro)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (BEFORE_EXIT)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_GUARD_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
      storeValueFromObject: (PLAYER), Mem(Afro), (SELF), Val(0)
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
  endLabel: 
  beginLabel: s32'end'
  sprite: s32'null', 5
  exitState: 
  beginLabel: s32'Bomb'
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
  specialAttack: 
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkLv2'
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(10000)
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(0)
  storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg13), Val(1)
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_hosei'
  damage: 0, 60
  tensionGainOnConnect: 0
  attackTarget: 1
  attackIgnoreCaution: 1
  attackCollisionForceExpand: 1
  hitEffectFire: 1
  groundHitEffect: (AIR_NORMAL)
  airHitEffect: (AIR_NORMAL)
  guardEffect: 1, s32''
  hitMainPlayerOnly: 1
  setProjectileDurability: 0
  attackReflect: 0
  attackFrontDirection: 3
  hitAirPushbackX: 0, 10000
  hitAirPushbackY: 0, 40000
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkGuardBreak'
  setGuardCrushDuration: 30
  attackCollisionForceExpand: 0
  hitMainPlayerOnly: 0
  onlyHitPlayer: 1
  hitCommonSfxAppend: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Expl_Fire_M'
  upon: (ALLY_GUARD)
    cmnSfx: s32'SE_BTL_CMN_Expl_Fire_M'
    createParticle: s32'cmn_guard_sp_simple', (FRONT_05_BODY)
  endUpon: 
  upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
    checkMoveFlag: (DEBUG)
    ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
      ifTrueInObject: (PLAYER), Mem(DmgFire)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(0)
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(15)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_AFTER_FIX_PARAM)
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  checkMoveFlag: (DEBUG)
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(600)
  endIf: 
  upon: (IDLING)
    ifNot: Mem(IsSomebodysCutSceneOrSelfHide)

              battleStats: s32'RCYellowNearAtk', 0, 1
            endRunOnObject: 
          endUpon: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(CmnCharaReg15), Val(2)
          upon: (RECEIVE_ATTACK)
            battleStats: s32'RCYellowFarDmg', 0, 1
            runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
              battleStats: s32'RCYellowFarAtk', 0, 1
            endRunOnObject: 
          endUpon: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (PRE_FRAME_STEP)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(CheckStop), Val(0)
      ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(4)
        modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(ActReg3), Val(-4)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(Tmp)
          modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(ActReg3), Val(0)
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(Tmp)
            tensionUsage: 720
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(4)
        modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(ActReg3), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(Tmp)
          modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(ActReg3), Val(7)
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(Tmp)
            tensionUsage: 200
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(OnIdlingTime), Val(24)
          tensionUsage: 5000
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
    if: Mem(ActReg6)
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(CmnCharaReg21)
        ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(500000)
          clearRegisteredUponCode: (NO_STOP_IDLING)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            timeSlow: 20
            slowdownEndOnHit: 1
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
            timeSlow: 60
            slowdownEndOnHit: 0
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
            timeSlow: 40
            slowdownEndOnHit: 1
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(4)
            timeSlow: 10
            slowdownEndOnHit: 1
            slowdownProration: 1
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    else: 
      ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg3)
        modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(ActReg4), Val(1)
        ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(Tmp)
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Mem(ActReg4)
            calcDistance: 32, 103, 23, 100
            storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Mem(Tmp)
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg5), Val(500000)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
              timeSlow: 10
              slowdownEndOnHit: 1
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
              timeSlow: 30
              slowdownEndOnHit: 0
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
              timeSlow: 20
              slowdownEndOnHit: 1
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(4)
              timeSlow: 5
              slowdownEndOnHit: 1
              slowdownProration: 1
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
  upon: (WALL_BREAK)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (WALL_BREAK)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (TIMER)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (SUPERFREEZE)
    superFreeze: 0, 119, 1, 1
  endUpon: 
  if: Mem(CmnCharaReg19)
    sendValuesToObject: 2, 391, 0, 0
    createObjectWithArg: s32'cmn_ThrowRCobj', (PLAYER)
  endIf: 
  callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_dll_Damage', Val(11), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
endSubroutine:

    attackIgnoreOutPower: 0
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(100000)
      modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(-100000)
      forcedComboScaleCount: 0
      riscConsume: 0
    endIf: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnNohosei'
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnNageWSBPoint'
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_screenshake', Val(3), Val(3), Val(0), Val(0)
    nextHitActionNAme: 32, s32'cmn_ThrowRCobj'
    runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
      displayModel: 1
      setObjectSize: 1000
      setDepth: 0
      setDepthSpeed: 0, 0
      pushPositionX: 
      pushPositionY: 
      pushVelocityX: 
      pushVelocityY: 
      pushGravity: 
      dustEndLockParamClear: 0, 0
      popPositionX: 
      popPositionY: 
    endRunOnObject: 
    runOnObject: (PLAYER)
      dustEndLockParamClear: 0, 0
    endRunOnObject: 
    ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(10000)
      moveToPosType: 32, 103
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg6), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    else: 
      moveToPosType: 3, 103
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(1000), Mem(ActReg1)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(100), Mem(ActReg2)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(10), Mem(ActReg3)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(CmnCharaReg19), Val(1), Mem(ActReg4)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(10), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(100), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(10), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(1000), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(100), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg3), Val(10), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(75000)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg4), Val(75000)
      storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Dir), (PLAYER), Mem(Dir)
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
        ifNot: Mem(Dir)
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg2)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg2)
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        ifNot: Mem(Dir)
          modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg2)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(PosXRaw), Mem(ActReg2)
        endElse: 
        flipDirection: 
      endElse: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg3), Val(1)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg4)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(PosY), Mem(ActReg4)
      endElse: 
      createParticle: s32'cmn_hit_m', (PLAYER)
    endElse: 
    storeValueFromObject: (PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg19), (SELF), Val(0)
    upon: (PLAYER_AFTER_EXECUTE_DAMAGE)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_AFTER_EXECUTE_DAMAGE)
      upon: (FRAME_STEP)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (FRAME_STEP)
        checkLastAttackHitStateName: 32, s32'cmn_ThrowRCobj'
        if: Mem(Tmp)
          runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
            ignoreSpeedTime: 6
          endRunOnObject: 
          if: Mem(ActReg6)
            runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
              popVelocityX: 
              popVelocityY: 
              popGravity: 
            endRunOnObject: 
            ifOperationInObject: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedX), Val(30000)
              runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
                physicsXImpulse: 0, 30000
              endRunOnObject: 
            endIf: 
            ifOperationInObject: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(SpeedY), Val(45000)
              runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
                physicsYImpulse: 0, 45000
              endRunOnObject: 
            endIf: 
            ifOperationInObject: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(Gravity), Val(1500)
              runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
                setGravity: 1500
              endRunOnObject: 
            endIf: 
            if: Mem(ActReg5)
              runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
                physicsXImpulse: 0, -5000
                physicsYImpulse: 0, 25000
              endRunOnObject: 
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endUpon: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(SentToObject0), Val(2)
        runOnObject: (PLAYER)
          flipDirection: 
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_PRIVATE)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (PLAYER_RECEIVE_ATTACK_PRIVATE)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg5), Val(1)
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'_burst_02', 5
  grabOrRelease: 
endState:

  endRunOnObject:

endSubroutine:

  endRunOnObject: 
  runOnObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER)
    timeSlow: 0
  endRunOnObject: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWorldStop_End'
  ignoreSuperFreezeFromAlly: 0
  enableRomanCancelMove: 1
  invulnForce: 0
  clearRegisteredUponCode: (WALL_BREAK)
  tensionCooldown: 180
  ignoreSpeed: 0
  if: Mem(FuncArg0)
    enableRomanCancelMove: 0
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(FuncArg1)
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_changecheck', Val(0), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmnWorldStop_Obj'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    deactivateObjectByNameExceptSelf: s32'cmnWorldStop_Obj'
    upon: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)
      ifNot: Mem(CheckStop)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)
        ifNot: Mem(SentToObject0)
          ifNot: Mem(SentToObject1)
            runOnObject: (PLAYER)
              callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnWorldStop_End', Val(0), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            runOnObject: (PLAYER)
              callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnWorldStop_End', Val(0), Val(1), Val(0), Val(0)
            endRunOnObject: 
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
        else: 
          ifNot: Mem(SentToObject1)
            runOnObject: (PLAYER)
              callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnWorldStop_End', Val(1), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          else: 
            runOnObject: (PLAYER)
              callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnWorldStop_End', Val(1), Val(1), Val(0), Val(0)
            endRunOnObject: 
          endElse: 
        endElse: 
        deactivateCurrentObject: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
    upon: (AFTER_EXIT)
      debugLogForScript: s32'ON_PLAYER_ACTION_CHANGE', 0, 0
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_EXIT)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)
      deactivateCurrentObject: 
    endUpon: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 2147483647
endState:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Event'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(6)

      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(4500)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6_4500'
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(8000)
      checkStageName: s16'WhiteHouse_PL'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(-1)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(2)

            endElse:

              ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
                storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
              endIf:

              endElse:

            else:

            endElse:

            checkBackgroundClashEventDone: s32'Box0_L'
            ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            endIf: 
            else: 
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(0)
            if: Mem(BattleDoing)
              checkBackgroundClashEventDone: s32'Box0_R'
              ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
                storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
              endIf: 
              else: 
                storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
              endElse: 
            endIf: 
            else: 
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(1)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(3)
            if: Mem(BattleDoing)
              checkBackgroundClashEventDone: s32'Box3_L'
              ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
                storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
              endIf: 
              else: 
                storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
              endElse: 
            endIf: 
            else: 
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
            endElse: 
          endIf:

            checkBackgroundClashEventDone: s32'Box3_R'
            ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            endIf: 
            else: 
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            endElse: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(0)
            if: Mem(BattleDoing)
              checkBackgroundClashEventDone: s32'Box0_L'
              ifNot: Mem(Tmp)
                storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
              endIf: 
              else: 
                storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
              endElse: 
            endIf: 
            else: 
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
            endElse: 
          endIf:

            checkBackgroundClashEventDone: s32'Box0_R'
            ifNot: Mem(Tmp)

            endIf: 
            else:

            endElse: 
          endIf: 
        endIf:

          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6_8000'
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_WH_Out'
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_WH_In'
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6_8000'
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_WH_In_Break'
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        else: 
          callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6_8000'
        endElse: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6_8000'
      endElse: 
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageSplitCount), Val(3)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(4500)
      callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_3_4500'
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(StageOffsetRadius), Val(21000)
      checkStageName: s16'Station_PL'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
        ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(1)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(-1)
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(0)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(1)
            storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_ST_OUT'
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_3_21000_ST'
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_ST_IN'
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_3_21000_ST'
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_ST_IN'
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_3_21000_ST'
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        else: 
          callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_3_21000'
        endElse: 
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
      endIf: 
      else: 
        callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_3_21000'
        storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(ActReg0)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_6'
    debugLogForScript: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_Error', 0, 0
  endIf: 
  else: 
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
  endElse: 
  voiceLine: s16'vxxx003'
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Settings'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)

              callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnWSB_Effect_NoStop_or_Delete', Val(0), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf:

    upon: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)
      ifNot: Mem(BattleDoing)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)
        ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
          callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
          ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(0)
            ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(3)
              deactivateObjectById: (SELF)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
    upon: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)
      ifNot: Mem(BattleDoing)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)

          callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'

                checkCurrentStateName: (PLAYER), s32'WinActionWait'
                if: Mem(Tmp)
                  clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)

            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endUpon: 
  endIf:

      ifNot: Mem(BattleDoing)
        clearRegisteredUponCode: (AFTER_FRAME_STEP_EX)

          callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Max'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
  if: Mem(ReturnValue)
    checkStageName: s16'WhiteHouse_PL'
    if: Mem(Tmp)
      if: Mem(BattleDoing)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(-1)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(2)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(21840000)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(10920000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(10920000)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(3)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(21840000)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(15287999)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(15287999)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(5)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(21840000)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(18564000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(18564000)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(0)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(17472000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(17472000)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(17472000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(17472000)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(1)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(3)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(21840000)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(16380000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(16380000)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(4)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(21840000)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(15287999)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(15287999)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(0)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(15287999)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(15287999)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(18564000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(18564000)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(1)
            callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(21840000)
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(17472000)
              storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(17472000)
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
        ifOperation: (IS_GREATER), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(2)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(13104000)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(13104000)
        endIf: 
        else: 
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
          storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(21840000)
        endElse: 
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Slave_Slide_WH_In'
  checkCurrentStateName: (SELF), s32'WSB_Slave_Bound'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'gorogoro'
  endIf: 
  else: 
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'loop'
  endElse: 
  createObject: s32'cmnWSB_Camera_Slide_6_8000', (PLAYER)
  resetMotionBlurAmount: 
  haltMomentum: 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(95)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(PosY), Val(2), Mem(ActReg1)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(21840000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Val(43680000)
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg4), Val(500000)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(-1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg2)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_GREATER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg3)
  endIf: 
  warp: (SELF), (WORLD_ZERO), Mem(ActReg4), Mem(ActReg1), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(ActReg0), Val(-1), Mem(ActReg6)
  modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(ActReg0)
  modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(Gravity)
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(0)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(-1)
      modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Val(60)
      modifyVar2: (SUB), Val(70000), Mem(Tmp)
      physicsYImpulse: 2, 0
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(1)
      modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Val(89)
      modifyVar2: (SUB), Val(30000), Mem(Tmp)
      physicsYImpulse: 2, 0
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(BoxIndex), Val(3)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(-1)
      modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Val(33)
      modifyVar2: (SUB), Val(90000), Mem(Tmp)
      physicsYImpulse: 2, 0
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(WSBMoveDir), Val(1)
      modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(PosY), Val(50)
      modifyVar2: (SUB), Val(70000), Mem(Tmp)
      physicsYImpulse: 2, 0
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  upon: (IDLING)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmnWSB_Event_Status'
    ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(ReturnValue), Val(1)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
      haltMomentum: 1
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(95)
      modifyVar: (SUB), Mem(ActReg0), Mem(ActionTime)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Mem(PosXRaw)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(85)
      modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ActReg2), Val(100)
      modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar2: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(-1)
      physicsXImpulseRaw: 2, 0
      physicsYImpulse: 0, 75000
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Mem(PosY)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg2), Val(2)
      modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActReg0)
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Mem(SpeedY)
      modifyVar: (MUL), Mem(ActReg3), Val(-2)
      modifyVar: (DIV), Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg0)
      modifyVar2: (SUB), Mem(ActReg2), Mem(ActReg3)
      storeValue: Mem(Gravity), Mem(Tmp)
      setGameSpeed: 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 48, s32'linear', s32'accel', 0
      landingHeight: 0
      upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
        gotoLabelRequests: s32'landing'
        haltMomentum: 1

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_WildAssault'
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg6), Mem(FuncArg0)
  resetInputCommand: 
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_AtkLv4'
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_countertype_middle'
  damage: 0, 30
  hitSoftKnockdown: 0
  ifNot: Mem(FuncArg3)
    damageEffect: 4, s32'cmn_wildassalut_hit'
    guardEffect: 4, s32'cmn_wildassalut_hit'
  endIf: 
  else: 
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_countertype_middle_slash'
    hitEffectSlash: 1
    damageEffect: 4, s32'cmn_wildassalut_slash'
    guardEffect: 4, s32'cmn_wildassalut_slash'
  endElse: 
  ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(2)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg13), Val(1)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_hosei'
  endIf: 
  else: 
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg11), Val(1000)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg12), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg13), Val(1)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_hosei'
  endElse: 
  riscConsume: 30
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(0)
    riscConsume: 40
  endIf: 
  callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_SameAttack', Val(1), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
  sameAttackAddGravity: 0, 2500
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(1)
    pushbackXForHit: 40
    groundHitEffect: (STAGGER)
    staggerDuration: 23
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(2)
    hitStop: 20
    pushbackX: 50
    groundHitEffect: (AIR_FACE_UP)
    hitAirPushbackX: 0, 20000
    hitAirPushbackY: 0, 30000
  endIf: 
  ignorePushbackXScaling: 1
  ignorePushbackYScaling: 1
  ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(2)
    enableJumpCancel: 1
  endIf: 
  upon: (HIT_OR_GUARD_ANY_OBJECT)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (HIT_OR_GUARD_ANY_OBJECT)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(1)
      extendPushboxX: 40000
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(2)
      enableNormals: 1
      enableSpecials: 1
      enableBackDash: 1
    endIf: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg7), Val(100)
      battleStats: s32'WildAssaultDelay_Hit', 0, 1
    endIf: 
    else: 
      battleStats: s32'WildAssault_Hit', 0, 1
    endElse: 
  endUpon: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(9)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(13)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(13)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(11)
  endIf: 
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg3), Mem(ActReg1)
  upon: (IDLING)
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActionTime), Val(3)
      if: Mem(BattleDoing)
        modifyBurstGauge: -7500
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(0)
        upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
          doNotBeginCancel: 1
          setInertia: 50000
          createObject: s32'cmn_wildassault_push', (CENTER)
        endUpon: 
      endIf: 
      ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(1)
        upon: (BEFORE_EXIT)
          doNotBeginCancel: 1
          setInertia: 20000

                  endElse: 
                endElse: 
              endElse: 
            endElse: 
          endElse: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_3on3_mainposcheck'
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg5), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosXRaw)
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosXRaw)
  ifOperation: (IS_LESSER), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(Tmp)
    returnValue: 0, 0
  endIf: 
  else: 
    returnValue: 0, 1
  endElse: 
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(ActReg5), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosXRaw)
  storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(PosXRaw)
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg5), Mem(Tmp)
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(Dir)
    returnValue: 2, 0
  endIf: 
  ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg29), Val(2)
    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(Dir)
    returnValue: 2, 0
  endIf: 
  ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CmnCharaReg29), Val(2)
    ifNotInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(Dir)
      returnValue: 0, 1
    endIf: 
    else: 
      returnValue: 0, 0
    endElse: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_3on3_Sub_Posz_Zline'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
    if: Mem(IsSubMember1Self)
      setDepth: -250000

      checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2), s32'3on3_s'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2), Mem(PosZ), Val(-250000)
          setDepth: -300000

          runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
            zLine: 6, 5
          endRunOnObject: 
        endIf: 
      endIf:

          zLine: 6, 5

    if: Mem(IsSubMember2Self)
      setDepth: -250000
      zLine: 6, 5
      checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1), s32'3on3_s'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1), Mem(PosZ), Val(-250000)
          setDepth: -300000
          zLine: 5, 5
          runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
            zLine: 6, 5
          endRunOnObject: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1), s32'3on3_r'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        setDepth: -250000
        zLine: 5, 5
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
          zLine: 6, 5
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
    if: Mem(IsSubMember1Self)
      setDepth: -100000
      zLine: 6, 5
      checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2), s32'3on3_s'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        setDepth: -100000
        zLine: 6, 5
        runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
          zLine: 5, 5
        endRunOnObject: 
      endIf: 
      checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2), s32'3on3_r'
      if: Mem(Tmp)
        ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2), Mem(PosZ), Val(-100000)
          setDepth: -150000
          zLine: 5, 5
          runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
            zLine: 6, 5
          endRunOnObject: 
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
    if: Mem(IsSubMember2Self)
      setDepth: -100000
      zLine: 6, 5
      checkCurrentStateName: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1), s32'3on3_s'

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_3on3_Skill_Create_Pre'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(0)
    sendValuesToObject: 2, 45, 2, 47
    createObjectWithArg: s32'cmn_to3_hatudo', (PLAYER)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_3on3_Skill_Create'
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginState: s32'cmn_to3_hatudo'
  upon: (IMMEDIATE)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Mem(SentToObject0)
    ifNot: Mem(SideID)
      linkParticle: s32'CMN_to3_hatudo01'
    endIf: 
    else: 
      linkParticle: s32'CMN_to3_hatudo02'
    endElse: 
    addPositionX: 0, 250000
    addPositionY: 0, 250000
    setDepth: 0
    zLine: 3, 5
    landingHeight: 0
    upon: (TOUCH_GROUND)
      haltMomentum: 1
    endUpon: 
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_to3_hatudo_Pattern', Val(1), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_TO3_Skill_Init'
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_TO3_Skill_WSB', Val(2), Val(4), Val(0), Val(0)
    upon: 105
      clearRegisteredUponCode: 105
      storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(1)
    endUpon: 
    ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(14)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: 105
    endIf: 
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 14
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  debugLogForScript: s32'pre', 0, 0
  endLabel: 
  beginLabel: s32'hatudo'
  sprite: s32'null', 60
  ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg3)
    ifNot: Mem(CmnCharaReg5)
      ifNot: Mem(ActReg2)
        callSubroutine: s32'cmn_3on3_Skill_Create'
      endIf: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
  ifNot: Mem(ActReg1)
    velocityXPercentEachFrame: 50
    velocityYPercentEachFrame: 50
  endIf: 
endState: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_to3_hatudo_Pattern'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(0)
    warp: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), (PLAYER_LAND), Val(0), Val(0), Val(15)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
    warp: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), (PLAYER), Val(250000), Val(250000), Val(15)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
    warp: (SELF), 168, Val(0), Val(250000), Val(15)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(4)
    warp: (SELF), (PLAYER), Val(250000), Val(750000), Val(15)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(5)
    homing: 0, 32, 123, 0, 0, 0, 750000, 0, 5, 0, 75
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(6)
    warp: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), (PLAYER_LAND), Val(250000), Val(0), Val(15)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(7)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(9)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(10)
    warp: (SELF), 168, Val(0), Val(250000), Val(15)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(14)
    warp: (SELF), 168, Val(0), Val(0), Val(15)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(16)
    homing: 0, 29, 103, 0, 0, 0, 75000, 0, 5, 0, 75
    addVelocityY: 0, -25000
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(18)
    homing: 0, 29, 103, 0, 0, 0, 75000, 0, 5, 0, 75
    addVelocityY: 0, -25000
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(20)
    homing: 0, 29, 103, 0, 0, 0, 75000, 0, 5, 0, 75
    addVelocityY: 0, -25000
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(22)
    homing: 0, 29, 103, 0, 0, 0, 75000, 0, 5, 0, 75
    addVelocityY: 0, -25000
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg1), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg0), Val(23)
    homing: 0, 29, 103, 0, 0, 0, 75000, 0, 5, 0, 75
    addVelocityY: 0, -25000

  if: Mem(FuncArg0)

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_TO3_Skill_Lv_RB'
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg7), Val(1)
    modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(SentToObject0), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(Tmp), Val(2)
    modifyVar2: (MUL), Mem(Tmp), Mem(FuncArg1)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(Tmp), Mem(FuncArg0), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(SentToObject0), Val(0)
    modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(Tmp), Val(2)
    modifyVar2: (MUL), Mem(Tmp), Mem(FuncArg3)
    modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(Tmp), Mem(FuncArg2)
    modifyVar2: (MUL), Mem(Tmp), Mem(SentToObject1)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg7), Mem(Tmp)
    debugLogForScript: s32'jizoku', 2, 52
  endIf: 
  else: 
    modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(SentToObject0), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(Tmp), Val(2)
    modifyVar2: (MUL), Mem(Tmp), Mem(FuncArg1)
    modifyVarAfterOperation: (ADD), Mem(Tmp), Mem(FuncArg0), Mem(ActReg7)
    modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(SentToObject0), Val(0)
    modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(Tmp), Val(2)
    modifyVar2: (MUL), Mem(Tmp), Mem(FuncArg3)
    modifyVar2: (ADD), Mem(Tmp), Mem(FuncArg2)
    modifyVar2: (MUL), Mem(Tmp), Mem(SentToObject1)
    modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg7), Mem(Tmp)
  endElse: 
endSubroutine:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_TO3_Skill_Recovery'
  ifNot: Mem(Timeup)
    ifTrueInObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(HitPoint)
      ifTrueInObject: (To3_ENEMY_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(HitPoint)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (DIV), Mem(SentToObject0), Val(2), Mem(ActReg6)
        modifyVarAfterOperation: (MUL), Mem(ActReg6), Mem(SentToObject1), Mem(ActReg7)
        modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(ActReg7), Mem(SentToObject1)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(0)
            runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
              modifyHPByRate: 0, 10
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(1)
            runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
              modifyHPByRate: 0, 11
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(2)
            runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
              modifyHPByRate: 0, 12
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg7), Val(1)
            runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
              modifyHPByRate: 0, 4
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg7), Val(2)
            runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
              modifyHPByRate: 0, 5
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg7), Val(3)
            runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
              modifyHPByRate: 0, 6
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(0)
            runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
              modifyHPByRate: 0, 15
            endRunOnObject:

          ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(ActReg6), Val(1)
            runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
              modifyHPByRate: 0, 16
            endRunOnObject:

              modifyHPByRate: 0, 17
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)

              addTensionUnscaled: 0, 2000
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf:

              addTensionUnscaled: 0, 2200
            endRunOnObject: 
          endIf:

    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (STACK0), Mem(SentToObject0)
    ifOperation: (IS_NOT_EQUAL), Mem(SentToObject0), Mem(Tmp)
      storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (STACK0), Mem(SentToObject1)
      modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(SentToObject1), Mem(Tmp)
    endIf: 
    sendSignal: (STACK0), (SELF)
  endIf: 
  upon: (SIGNAL0)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg2), Val(1)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (SIGNAL0)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
    clearRegisteredUponCode: (BEFORE_EXIT)
    gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
  endUpon: 
  sprite: s32'null', 1
  storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
  findState: s32'cmn_TO3_Skill_23_sub01', 4, 2, 45

    storeValueFromObject: (SELF), Mem(Tmp), (STACK0), Mem(SentToObject0)

      storeValue: Mem(SentToObject0), Val(0)
    endIf:

    endIf: 
    ifNot: Mem(SentToObject1)
      clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
    endIf:

      clearRegisteredUponCode: (IDLING)
      gotoLabelRequests: s32'end'
    endIf:

      modifyHP: 5
    endIf:

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_3on3_Rannyu_Check'
  checkCurrentStateEntryName: s32'3on3_r_1'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(1)
  endIf: 
  checkCurrentStateEntryName: s32'3on3_r_2'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(2)
  endIf: 
  checkCurrentStateEntryName: s32'3on3_r_3'
  if: Mem(Tmp)
    storeValue: Mem(ActReg0), Val(3)
  endIf: 
endSubroutine: 

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_TO3_RannyuAtk_Init'
  if: Mem(IsPlayer)
    attackAllDefault: 
    initializeAttackCategory: 18, 1
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(0)
    attackLevel: 0
    hitstunAmount: 12
    blockstunAmount: 9
    riscGain: 5
    hitStop: 11
    tensionGainOnConnect: 30
    preGuardRange: 0, 190
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnAtk_GB_TGG', Mem(FuncArg1), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(1), Val(0)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(1)
    attackLevel: 1
    hitstunAmount: 14
    blockstunAmount: 11
    riscGain: 10
    hitStop: 12
    tensionGainOnConnect: 40
    preGuardRange: 0, 195
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnAtk_GB_TGG', Mem(FuncArg1), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(2), Val(0)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(2)
    attackLevel: 2
    hitstunAmount: 16
    blockstunAmount: 13
    riscGain: 15
    hitStop: 13
    tensionGainOnConnect: 50
    preGuardRange: 0, 200
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnAtk_GB_TGG', Mem(FuncArg1), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(3), Val(0)
  endIf: 
  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(3)
    attackLevel: 3
    hitstunAmount: 19
    blockstunAmount: 16
    riscGain: 20
    hitStop: 14
    tensionGainOnConnect: 60
    preGuardRange: 0, 205
    callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmnAtk_GB_TGG', Mem(FuncArg1), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(4), Val(0)

  ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg0), Val(4)
    attackLevel: 4

    tensionGainOnConnect: 70

  endIf: 
  callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv0'
  if: Mem(FuncArg1)
    storeValue: Mem(CmnCharaReg13), Mem(FuncArg1)
    callSubroutine: s32'cmn_WSBPoint_Add_Lv3'
  endIf: 
  damage: 0, 1
  fuwafuwa: 0

beginSubroutine: s32'cmn_TO3CPUEstimate'
  if: Mem(IsTo3)
    if: Mem(To3IsTurorial)
      ifNot: Mem(FuncArg0)
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(To3TutorialPhase), Val(1)
          callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_TO3CPUEstimate', Val(1), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(To3TutorialPhase), Val(2)
          callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_TO3CPUEstimate', Val(1), Val(0), Val(0), Val(0)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(To3TutorialPhase), Val(3)
          callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_TO3CPUEstimate', Val(1), Val(1), Val(0), Val(0)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(To3TutorialPhase), Val(4)
          callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_TO3CPUEstimate', Val(1), Val(2), Val(0), Val(0)
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(To3TutorialPhase), Val(5)
          callSubroutineWithArgs: s32'cmn_TO3CPUEstimate', Val(1), Val(3), Val(0), Val(0)
        endIf: 
      endIf: 
      else: 
        if: Mem(IsCPU)
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_s'
            addMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_r_1'
            addMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_r_2'
            addMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_r_3'
            addMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_k_1'
            addMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_k_4'
            addMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(1)
          ifNot: Mem(SideID)
            moveRewriteMode: 1
            addMove: s32'3on3_k_1'
              removeMoveFlag: 120
              cpuEstimatePoint: 150
              cpuEstimateInterval: 60
              moveEstChusenMorePercent: 0
            endMove: 
            ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(1)
              moveRewriteMode: 1
              addMove: s32'3on3_k_4'
                removeMoveFlag: 120
                cpuEstimatePoint: 150
                cpuEstimateInterval: 60
                moveEstChusenMorePercent: 0
              endMove: 
            endIf: 
            ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(2)
              moveRewriteMode: 1
              addMove: s32'3on3_k_1'
                addMoveFlag: 120
              endMove: 
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg2), Val(1)
              runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
                modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(1)
              endRunOnObject: 
              runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
                modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(1)
              endRunOnObject: 
              runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
                modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(1)
              endRunOnObject: 
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(2)
          ifNot: Mem(SideID)
            moveRewriteMode: 1
            addMove: s32'3on3_k_4'
              removeMoveFlag: 120
              cpuEstimatePoint: 150
              cpuEstimateInterval: 60
              moveEstChusenMorePercent: 0
            endMove: 
            ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(1)
              moveRewriteMode: 1
              addMove: s32'3on3_k_1'
                removeMoveFlag: 120
                cpuEstimatePoint: 150
                cpuEstimateInterval: 60
                moveEstChusenMorePercent: 0
              endMove: 
            endIf: 
            ifOperationInObject: (IS_EQUAL), (To3_MAIN_PLAYER), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(2)
              moveRewriteMode: 1
              addMove: s32'3on3_k_1'
                addMoveFlag: 120
              endMove: 
            endIf: 
            ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg2), Val(1)
              runOnObject: (To3_MAIN_PLAYER)
                modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(1)
              endRunOnObject: 
              runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_1)
                modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(1)
              endRunOnObject: 
              runOnObject: (To3_ASSIST_PLAYER_2)
                modifyVar: (ADD), Mem(CPUVal0), Val(1)
              endRunOnObject: 
            endIf: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
        ifOperation: (IS_EQUAL), Mem(FuncArg1), Val(3)
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_s'
            removeMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_r_1'
            removeMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_r_2'
            removeMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          moveRewriteMode: 1
          addMove: s32'3on3_r_3'
            removeMoveFlag: 120
          endMove: 
          modifyVar2: (MUL), Mem(HitPointMax), Val(75)
          modifyVar2: (DIV), Mem(Tmp), Val(100)
          ifOperation: (IS_LESSER_OR_EQUAL), Mem(HitPoint), Mem(Tmp)
            moveRewriteMode: 1
            addMove: s32'3on3_k_1'
              removeMoveFlag: 120
              cpuEstimatePoint: 75
              cpuEstimateInterval: 300
              moveEstChusenMorePercent: 25
            endMove: 
            moveRewriteMode: 1
            addMove: s32'3on3_k_4'
              removeMoveFlag: 120
              cpuEstimatePoint: 75
              cpuEstimateInterval: 300
              moveEstChusenMorePercent: 25
            endMove: 
          endIf: 
        endIf: 
      endElse: 
    endIf: 
  endIf: 
endSubroutine:
